3332 void RigSpawner::ProcessTrigger(RigDef::Trigger & def)
3333 {
3334  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
3335 
3336  if (! CheckBeamLimit(1) || ! CheckShockLimit(1))
3337  {
3338  return;
3339  }
3340 
3341  shock_t & shock = this->GetFreeShock();
3342 
3343  // Disable trigger on startup? (default enabled)
3344  shock.trigger_enabled = !def.HasFlag_x_StartDisabled();
3345 
3346  m_rig->commandkey[def.shortbound_trigger_action].trigger_cmdkeyblock_state = false;
3347  if (def.longbound_trigger_action != -1)
3348  {
3349  m_rig->commandkey[def.longbound_trigger_action].trigger_cmdkeyblock_state = false;
3350  }
3351 
3352  unsigned int hydro_type = BEAM_HYDRO;
3353  unsigned int shock_flags = SHOCK_FLAG_NORMAL | SHOCK_FLAG_ISTRIGGER;
3354  float short_limit = def.contraction_trigger_limit;
3355  float long_limit = def.expansion_trigger_limit;
3356 
3357  if (def.HasFlag_i_Invisible())
3358  {
3359  hydro_type = BEAM_INVISIBLE_HYDRO;
3360  BITMASK_SET_1(shock_flags, SHOCK_FLAG_INVISIBLE);
3361  }
3362  if (def.HasFlag_B_TriggerBlocker())
3363  {
3364  BITMASK_SET_1(shock_flags, SHOCK_FLAG_TRG_BLOCKER);
3365  }
3366  if (def.HasFlag_s_CmdNumSwitch()) // switch that exchanges cmdshort/cmdshort for all triggers with the same commandnumbers, default false
3367  {
3368  BITMASK_SET_1(shock_flags, SHOCK_FLAG_TRG_CMD_SWITCH);
3369  }
3370  if (def.HasFlag_c_CommandStyle()) // // trigger is set with commandstyle boundaries instead of shocksytle
3371  {
3372  short_limit = abs(short_limit - 1);
3373  long_limit = long_limit - 1;
3374  }
3375  if (def.HasFlag_A_InvTriggerBlocker()) // Blocker that enable/disable other triggers, reversed activation method (inverted Blocker style, auto-ON)
3376  {
3377  BITMASK_SET_1(shock_flags, SHOCK_FLAG_TRG_BLOCKER_A);
3378  }
3379  if (def.HasFlag_h_UnlocksHookGroup())
3380  {
3381  BITMASK_SET_1(shock_flags, SHOCK_FLAG_TRG_HOOK_UNLOCK);
3382  }
3383  if (def.HasFlag_H_LocksHookGroup())
3384  {
3385  BITMASK_SET_1(shock_flags, SHOCK_FLAG_TRG_HOOK_LOCK);
3386  }
3387  if (def.HasFlag_t_Continuous())
3388  {
3389  BITMASK_SET_1(shock_flags, SHOCK_FLAG_TRG_CONTINUOUS); // this trigger sends values between 0 and 1
3390  }
3391  if (def.HasFlag_E_EngineTrigger())
3392  {
3393  BITMASK_SET_1(shock_flags, SHOCK_FLAG_TRG_ENGINE);
3394  }
3395 
3396  // Checks
3397  if (!def.IsTriggerBlockerAnyType() && !def.IsHookToggleTrigger() && !def.HasFlag_E_EngineTrigger())
3398  {
3399  if (def.shortbound_trigger_action < 1 || def.shortbound_trigger_action > MAX_COMMANDS)
3400  {
3401  std::stringstream msg;
3402  msg << "Invalid value of 'shortbound_trigger_action': '" << def.shortbound_trigger_action << "'. Must be between 1 and "<<MAX_COMMANDS<<". Ignoring trigger.";
3403  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_ERROR, msg.str());
3404  return;
3405  }
3406  }
3407  else if (!def.IsHookToggleTrigger() && !def.HasFlag_E_EngineTrigger())
3408  {
3409  // this is a Trigger-Blocker, make special check
3410  if (def.shortbound_trigger_action < 0 || def.longbound_trigger_action < 0)
3411  {
3412  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_ERROR, "Wrong command-eventnumber (Triggers). Trigger-Blocker deactivated.");
3413  return;
3414  }
3415  }
3416  else if (def.HasFlag_E_EngineTrigger())
3417  {
3418  if (def.IsTriggerBlockerAnyType() || def.IsHookToggleTrigger() || def.HasFlag_s_CmdNumSwitch())
3419  {
3420  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_ERROR, "Wrong command-eventnumber (Triggers). Engine trigger deactivated.");
3421  return;
3422  }
3423  }
3424 
3425  int node_1_index = FindNodeIndex(def.nodes[0]);
3426  int node_2_index = FindNodeIndex(def.nodes[1]);
3427  if (node_1_index == -1 || node_2_index == -1 )
3428  {
3429  return;
3430  }
3431  int beam_index = m_rig->free_beam;
3432  beam_t & beam = AddBeam(GetNode(node_1_index), GetNode(node_2_index), def.beam_defaults, def.detacher_group);
3433  beam.type = hydro_type;
3434  SetBeamStrength(beam, def.beam_defaults->breaking_threshold_constant);
3435  SetBeamSpring(beam, 0.f);
3436  SetBeamDamping(beam, 0.f);
3437  CalculateBeamLength(beam);
3438  beam.shortbound = short_limit;
3439  beam.longbound = long_limit;
3440  beam.bounded = SHOCK2;
3441  beam.shock = &shock;
3442  beam.diameter = DEFAULT_BEAM_DIAMETER;
3443 
3444  CreateBeamVisuals(beam, beam_index, def.beam_defaults, hydro_type != BEAM_INVISIBLE_HYDRO);
3445 
3446  if (m_rig->triggerdebug)
3447  {
3448  LOG("Trigger added. BeamID " + TOSTRING(beam_index));
3449  }
3450 
3451  shock.beamid = beam_index;
3452  shock.trigger_switch_state = 0.0f; // used as bool and countdowntimer, dont touch!
3453 
3454  if (!def.IsTriggerBlockerAnyType())
3455  {
3456  shock.trigger_cmdshort = def.shortbound_trigger_action;
3457  if (def.longbound_trigger_action != -1 || (def.longbound_trigger_action == -1 && def.IsHookToggleTrigger()))
3458  {
3459  // this is a trigger or a hook_toggle
3460  shock.trigger_cmdlong = def.longbound_trigger_action;
3461  }
3462  else
3463  {
3464  // this is a commandkeyblocker
3465  shock_flags |= SHOCK_FLAG_TRG_CMD_BLOCKER;
3466  }
3467  }
3468  else
3469  {
3470  // this is a trigger_blocker
3471  if (!def.HasFlag_A_InvTriggerBlocker())
3472  {
3473  //normal BLOCKER
3474  shock_flags |= SHOCK_FLAG_TRG_BLOCKER;
3475  shock.trigger_cmdshort = def.shortbound_trigger_action;
3476  shock.trigger_cmdlong = def.longbound_trigger_action;
3477  }
3478  else
3479  {
3480  //inverted BLOCKER
3481  shock_flags |= SHOCK_FLAG_TRG_BLOCKER_A;
3482  shock.trigger_cmdshort = def.shortbound_trigger_action;
3483  shock.trigger_cmdlong = def.longbound_trigger_action;
3484  }
3485  }
3486 
3487  if (def.HasFlag_b_KeyBlocker() && !def.HasFlag_B_TriggerBlocker())
3488  {
3489  m_rig->commandkey[def.shortbound_trigger_action].trigger_cmdkeyblock_state = true;
3490  if (def.longbound_trigger_action != -1)
3491  {
3492  m_rig->commandkey[def.longbound_trigger_action].trigger_cmdkeyblock_state = true;
3493  }
3494  }
3495 
3496  shock.trigger_boundary_t = def.boundary_timer;
3497  shock.flags = shock_flags;
3498  shock.sbd_spring = def.beam_defaults->springiness;
3499  shock.sbd_damp = def.beam_defaults->damping_constant;
3500  shock.last_debug_state = 0;
3501 
3502 }

3514 void RigSpawner::ProcessRotator(RigDef::Rotator & def)
3515 {

3517 
3518  if (! CheckRotatorLimit(1))
3519  {
3520  return;
3521  }
3522 
3523  unsigned int rotator_index = m_rig->free_rotator;
3524  m_rig->free_rotator++;
3525  rotator_t & rotator = m_rig->rotators[rotator_index];
3526 
3527  rotator.angle = 0;
3528  rotator.rate = def.rate;
3529  rotator.axis1 = GetNodeIndexOrThrow(def.axis_nodes[0]);
3530  rotator.axis2 = GetNodeIndexOrThrow(def.axis_nodes[1]);
3531  rotator.force = ROTATOR_FORCE_DEFAULT;
3532  rotator.tolerance = ROTATOR_TOLERANCE_DEFAULT;
3533  rotator.rotatorEngineCoupling = def.engine_coupling;
3534  rotator.rotatorNeedsEngine = def.needs_engine;
3535  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < 4; i++)
3536  {
3537  rotator.nodes1[i] = GetNodeIndexOrThrow(def.base_plate_nodes[i]);
3538  rotator.nodes2[i] = GetNodeIndexOrThrow(def.rotating_plate_nodes[i]);
3539  }
3540 
3541  /* Rotate left key */
3542  m_rig->commandkey[def.spin_left_key].rotators.push_back(- (static_cast<int>(rotator_index) + 1));
3543  m_rig->commandkey[def.spin_left_key].description = "Rotate_Left/Right";
3544

3547 
3548  _ProcessCommandKeyInertia(def.inertia, *def.inertia_defaults, def.spin_left_key, def.spin_right_key);
3549 
3550  m_rig->hascommands = 1;

3599 void RigSpawner::_ProcessCommandKeyInertia(

3604 )

3634  inertia.stop_delay_factor,
3635  start_function,
3636  stop_function
3637  );
3638  }
3639  else if (inertia._start_delay_factor_set || inertia._stop_delay_factor_set)
3640  {
3641  m_rig->cmdInertia->setCmdKeyDelay(
3642  contract_key,

3644  inertia_defaults.stop_delay_factor,
3645  inertia_defaults.start_function,
3646  inertia_defaults.stop_function
3647  );
3648

3650  extend_key,

3660 void RigSpawner::ProcessCommand(RigDef::Command2 & def)
3661 {
3662  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
3663 
3664  if (! CheckBeamLimit(1))
3665  {
3666  return;
3667  }
3668 
3669  int beam_index = m_rig->free_beam;
3670  int node_1_index = FindNodeIndex(def.nodes[0]);
3671  int node_2_index = FindNodeIndex(def.nodes[1]);
3672  if (node_1_index == -1 || node_2_index == -1)
3673  {
3674  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_ERROR, "Failed to fetch node");
3675  return;
3676  }
3677  beam_t & beam = AddBeam(m_rig->nodes[node_1_index], m_rig->nodes[node_2_index], def.beam_defaults, def.detacher_group);
3678  CalculateBeamLength(beam);
3679  SetBeamStrength(beam, def.beam_defaults->GetScaledBreakingThreshold()); /* Override settings from AddBeam() */
3680  SetBeamSpring(beam, def.beam_defaults->GetScaledSpringiness());
3681  SetBeamDamping(beam, def.beam_defaults->GetScaledDamping());
3682  beam.type = BEAM_HYDRO;
3683 
3684  /* Options */
3685  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.options, RigDef::Command2::OPTION_i_INVISIBLE)) {
3686  beam.type = BEAM_INVISIBLE_HYDRO;
3687  }
3688  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.options, RigDef::Command2::OPTION_r_ROPE)) {
3689  beam.bounded = ROPE;
3690  }
3691  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.options, RigDef::Command2::OPTION_p_PRESS_ONCE)) {
3692  beam.isOnePressMode = 1;
3693  }
3694  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.options, RigDef::Command2::OPTION_o_PRESS_ONCE_CENTER)) {
3695  beam.isOnePressMode = 2;
3696  }
3697  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.options, RigDef::Command2::OPTION_f_NOT_FASTER)) {
3698  beam.isForceRestricted = true;
3699  }
3700  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.options, RigDef::Command2::OPTION_c_AUTO_CENTER)) {
3701  beam.isCentering = true;
3702  }
3703 
3704  beam.commandRatioShort = def.shorten_rate;
3705  beam.commandRatioLong = def.lengthen_rate;
3706  beam.commandShort = def.max_contraction;
3707  beam.commandLong = def.max_extension;
3708  beam.commandEngineCoupling = def.affect_engine;
3709  beam.commandNeedsEngine = def.needs_engine;
3710 
3711  /* set the middle of the command, so its not required to recalculate this everytime ... */
3712  if (def.max_extension > def.max_contraction)
3713  {
3714  beam.centerLength = (def.max_extension - def.max_contraction) / 2 + def.max_contraction;
3715  }
3716  else
3717  {
3718  beam.centerLength = (def.max_contraction - def.max_extension) / 2 + def.max_extension;
3719  }
3720 
3721  _ProcessCommandKeyInertia(def.inertia, *def.inertia_defaults, def.contract_key, def.extend_key);
3722 
3723  /* Add keys */
3724  command_t* contract_command = &m_rig->commandkey[def.contract_key];
3725  contract_command->beams.push_back(-beam_index);
3726  if (contract_command->description.empty())
3727  {
3728  contract_command->description = def.description;
3729  }
3730 
3731  command_t* extend_command = &m_rig->commandkey[def.extend_key];
3732  extend_command->beams.push_back(beam_index);
3733  if (extend_command->description.empty())
3734  {
3735  extend_command->description = def.description;
3736  }
3737 
3738  bool attach_to_scene = (beam.type != BEAM_VIRTUAL && beam.type != BEAM_INVISIBLE && beam.type != BEAM_INVISIBLE_HYDRO);
3739  CreateBeamVisuals(beam, beam_index, def.beam_defaults, attach_to_scene);
3740 
3741  m_rig->free_commands++;
3742  m_rig->hascommands = 1;
3743 }
3744 
3745 void RigSpawner::ProcessAnimator(RigDef::Animator & def)
3746 {
3747  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
3748 
3749  if (! CheckBeamLimit(1) || ! CheckHydroLimit(1))
3750  {
3751  return;
3752  }
3753 
3754  if (m_rig->hydroInertia != nullptr)
3755  {
3756  if (def.inertia_defaults->start_delay_factor > 0 && def.inertia_defaults->stop_delay_factor > 0)
3757  {
3758  m_rig->hydroInertia->setCmdKeyDelay(
3759  m_rig->free_hydro,
3760  def.inertia_defaults->start_delay_factor,
3761  def.inertia_defaults->stop_delay_factor,
3762  def.inertia_defaults->start_function,
3763  def.inertia_defaults->stop_function
3764  );
3765  }
3766  }
3767 
3768  unsigned int hydro_type = BEAM_HYDRO;
3769  unsigned int anim_flags = 0;
3770  float anim_option = 0;
3771 
3772  /* Options. '{' intentionally misplaced. */

3899  {
3900  beam.shortbound = def.short_limit;
3901  }
3902  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.flags, RigDef::Animator::OPTION_LONG_LIMIT))
3903  {
3904  beam.longbound = def.long_limit;
3905  }
3906 
3907  m_rig->hydro[m_rig->free_hydro] = beam_index;
3908  m_rig->free_hydro++;
3909 }

3911 beam_t & RigSpawner::AddBeam(
3912  node_t & node_1,
3913  node_t & node_2,
3914  boost::shared_ptr<RigDef::BeamDefaults> & beam_defaults,
3915  int detacher_group
3916 )
3917 {
3918  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
3919 
3920  /* Init */
3921  beam_t & beam = GetAndInitFreeBeam(node_1, node_2);
3922  beam.detacher_group = detacher_group;
3923  beam.diameter = beam_defaults->visual_beam_diameter;
3924  beam.disabled = false;
3925 
3926  /* Breaking threshold (strength) */
3927  float strength = beam_defaults->breaking_threshold_constant;
3928  beam.strength = strength;
3929  beam.iStrength = strength;
3930 
3931  /* Deformation */
3932  SetBeamDeformationThreshold(beam, beam_defaults);
3933 
3934  float plastic_coef = beam_defaults->plastic_deformation_coefficient;
3935  beam.plastic_coef = plastic_coef;
3936  beam.default_plastic_coef = plastic_coef;
3937 
3938  return beam;
3939 }

3945  beam.strength = strength;
3946  beam.iStrength = strength;

3949 void RigSpawner::ProcessHydro(RigDef::Hydro & def)
3950 {
3951  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
3952 
3953  if (! CheckHydroLimit(1) || ! CheckBeamLimit(1))
3954  {
3955  return;
3956  }
3957 
3958  unsigned int hydro_type = BEAM_HYDRO;
3959  unsigned int hydro_flags = 0;
3960 
3961  // Parse options
3962  if (def.options.empty()) // Parse as if option 'n' (OPTION_n_NORMAL) was present
3963  {
3964  hydro_type = BEAM_HYDRO;
3965  hydro_flags |= HYDRO_FLAG_DIR;
3966  }
3967  else
3968  {
3969  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < def.options.length(); ++i)
3970  {
3971  const char c = def.options[i];
3972  switch (c)
3973  {
3974  case RigDef::Hydro::OPTION_i_INVISIBLE: // i
3975  hydro_type = BEAM_INVISIBLE_HYDRO;
3976  break;
3977  case RigDef::Hydro::OPTION_n_NORMAL: // n
3978  hydro_type = BEAM_HYDRO;
3979  hydro_flags |= HYDRO_FLAG_DIR;
3980  break;
3981  case RigDef::Hydro::OPTION_s_DISABLE_ON_HIGH_SPEED: // 's': // speed changing hydro
3982  hydro_flags |= HYDRO_FLAG_SPEED;
3983  break;
3984  case RigDef::Hydro::OPTION_a_INPUT_AILERON: // 'a':
3985  hydro_flags |= HYDRO_FLAG_AILERON;
3986  break;
3987  case RigDef::Hydro::OPTION_r_INPUT_RUDDER: // 'r':
3988  hydro_flags |= HYDRO_FLAG_RUDDER;
3989  break;
3990  case RigDef::Hydro::OPTION_e_INPUT_ELEVATOR: // 'e':
3991  hydro_flags |= HYDRO_FLAG_ELEVATOR;
3992  break;
3993  case RigDef::Hydro::OPTION_u_INPUT_AILERON_ELEVATOR: // 'u':
3994  hydro_flags |= (HYDRO_FLAG_AILERON | HYDRO_FLAG_ELEVATOR);
3995  break;
3996  case RigDef::Hydro::OPTION_v_INPUT_InvAILERON_ELEVATOR: // 'v':
3997  hydro_flags |= (HYDRO_FLAG_REV_AILERON | HYDRO_FLAG_ELEVATOR);
3998  break;
3999  case RigDef::Hydro::OPTION_x_INPUT_AILERON_RUDDER: // 'x':
4000  hydro_flags |= (HYDRO_FLAG_AILERON | HYDRO_FLAG_RUDDER);
4001  break;
4002  case RigDef::Hydro::OPTION_y_INPUT_InvAILERON_RUDDER: // 'y':
4003  hydro_flags |= (HYDRO_FLAG_REV_AILERON | HYDRO_FLAG_RUDDER);
4004  break;
4005  case RigDef::Hydro::OPTION_g_INPUT_ELEVATOR_RUDDER: // 'g':
4006  hydro_flags |= (HYDRO_FLAG_ELEVATOR | HYDRO_FLAG_RUDDER);
4007  break;
4008  case RigDef::Hydro::OPTION_h_INPUT_InvELEVATOR_RUDDER: // 'h':
4009  hydro_flags |= (HYDRO_FLAG_REV_ELEVATOR | HYDRO_FLAG_RUDDER);
4010  break;
4011  default:
4012  this->AddMessage(Message::TYPE_WARNING, std::string("Ignoring invalid flag:") + c);
4013  break;
4014  }
4015 
4016  // NOTE: This is a quirk ported from v0.4.0.7 spawner (for compatibility)
4017  // This code obviously belongs after the options-loop.
4018  // However, since it's inside the loop, it only works correctly if the 'i' flag is last.
4019  //
4020  // ORIGINAL COMMENT: if you use the i flag on its own, add the direction to it
4021  if (hydro_type == BEAM_INVISIBLE_HYDRO && !hydro_flags)
4022  {
4023  hydro_flags |= HYDRO_FLAG_DIR;
4024  }
4025  }
4026  }
4027 
4028  /* Inertia */
4029  if (m_rig->hydroInertia != nullptr)
4030  {
4031  if (def.inertia._start_delay_factor_set && def.inertia._stop_delay_factor_set)
4032  {
4033  m_rig->hydroInertia->setCmdKeyDelay(
4034  m_rig->free_hydro,
4035  def.inertia_defaults->start_delay_factor,
4036  def.inertia_defaults->stop_delay_factor,
4037  def.inertia_defaults->start_function,
4038  def.inertia_defaults->stop_function
4039  );
4040  }
4041  else if (def.inertia._start_delay_factor_set || def.inertia._stop_delay_factor_set)
4042  {
4043  m_rig->hydroInertia->setCmdKeyDelay(
4044  m_rig->free_hydro,
4045  def.inertia_defaults->start_delay_factor,
4046  def.inertia_defaults->stop_delay_factor,
4047  def.inertia_defaults->start_function,
4048  def.inertia_defaults->stop_function
4049  );
4050  }
4051  }
4052 
4053  int beam_index = m_rig->free_beam;
4054  beam_t & beam = GetAndInitFreeBeam(GetNode(def.nodes[0]), GetNode(def.nodes[1]));
4055  SetBeamStrength(beam, def.beam_defaults->GetScaledBreakingThreshold());
4056  CalculateBeamLength(beam);
4057  SetBeamDeformationThreshold(beam, def.beam_defaults);
4058  beam.type = hydro_type;
4059  beam.k = def.beam_defaults->GetScaledSpringiness();
4060  beam.d = def.beam_defaults->GetScaledDamping();
4061  beam.detacher_group = def.detacher_group;
4062  beam.hydroFlags = hydro_flags;
4063  beam.hydroRatio = def.lenghtening_factor;
4064  beam.plastic_coef = def.beam_defaults->plastic_deformation_coefficient;
4065  beam.default_plastic_coef = def.beam_defaults->plastic_deformation_coefficient;
4066  beam.diameter = DEFAULT_BEAM_DIAMETER;
4067 
4068  CreateBeamVisuals(beam, beam_index, def.beam_defaults, (hydro_type == BEAM_INVISIBLE_HYDRO));
4069 
4070  m_rig->hydro[m_rig->free_hydro] = beam_index;
4071  m_rig->free_hydro++;
4072 }
4073 
4074 void RigSpawner::ProcessShock2(RigDef::Shock2 & def)
4075 {
4076  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
4077 
4078  if (! CheckShockLimit(1) || ! CheckBeamLimit(1))
4079  {
4080  return;
4081  }
4082 
4083  node_t & node_1 = GetNode(def.nodes[0]);
4084  node_t & node_2 = GetNode(def.nodes[1]);
4085  float short_bound = def.short_bound;
4086  float long_bound = def.long_bound;
4087  unsigned int hydro_type = BEAM_HYDRO;
4088  unsigned int shock_flags = SHOCK_FLAG_NORMAL | SHOCK_FLAG_ISSHOCK2;
4089 
4090  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.options, RigDef::Shock2::OPTION_i_INVISIBLE))
4091  {
4092  BITMASK_SET_1(shock_flags, SHOCK_FLAG_INVISIBLE);
4093  hydro_type = BEAM_INVISIBLE_HYDRO;
4094  }
4095  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.options, RigDef::Shock2::OPTION_s_SOFT_BUMP_BOUNDS))
4096  {
4097  BITMASK_SET_0(shock_flags, SHOCK_FLAG_NORMAL); /* Not normal anymore */
4098  BITMASK_SET_1(shock_flags, SHOCK_FLAG_SOFTBUMP);
4099  }
4100  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.options, RigDef::Shock2::OPTION_m_METRIC))
4101  {
4102  float beam_length = node_1.AbsPosition.distance(node_2.AbsPosition);
4103  short_bound /= beam_length;
4104  long_bound /= beam_length;
4105  }
4106  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.options, RigDef::Shock2::OPTION_M_ABSOLUTE_METRIC))
4107  {
4108  float beam_length = node_1.AbsPosition.distance(node_2.AbsPosition);
4109  short_bound = (beam_length - short_bound) / beam_length;
4110  long_bound = (long_bound - beam_length) / beam_length;
4111 
4112  if (long_bound < 0.f)
4113  {
4114  AddMessage(
4115  Message::TYPE_WARNING,
4116  "Metric shock length calculation failed, 'short_bound' less than beams spawn length. Resetting to beam's spawn length (short_bound = 0)"
4117  );
4118  long_bound = 0.f;
4119  }
4120 
4121  if (short_bound > 1.f)
4122  {
4123  AddMessage(
4124  Message::TYPE_WARNING,
4125  "Metric shock length calculation failed, 'short_bound' less than 0 meters. Resetting to 0 meters (short_bound = 1)"
4126  );
4127  short_bound = 1.f;
4128  }
4129  }
4130 
4131  int beam_index = m_rig->free_beam;
4132  beam_t & beam = GetAndInitFreeBeam(node_1, node_2);
4133  SetBeamStrength(beam, def.beam_defaults->breaking_threshold_constant * 4.f);
4134  SetBeamDeformationThreshold(beam, def.beam_defaults);
4135  beam.type = hydro_type;
4136  beam.bounded = SHOCK2;
4137  beam.k = def.spring_in;
4138  beam.d = def.damp_in;
4139  beam.shortbound = short_bound;
4140  beam.longbound = long_bound;
4141  beam.plastic_coef = def.beam_defaults->plastic_deformation_coefficient;
4142  beam.default_plastic_coef = def.beam_defaults->plastic_deformation_coefficient;
4143  beam.diameter = DEFAULT_BEAM_DIAMETER;
4144 
4145  /* Length + pre-compression */
4146  CalculateBeamLength(beam);
4147  beam.L *= def.precompression;
4148  beam.refL *= def.precompression;
4149  beam.Lhydro *= def.precompression;
4150 
4151  CreateBeamVisuals(beam, beam_index, def.beam_defaults, hydro_type != BEAM_INVISIBLE_HYDRO);
4152 
4153  shock_t & shock = GetFreeShock();
4154  shock.flags = shock_flags;
4155  shock.sbd_spring = def.beam_defaults->springiness;
4156  shock.sbd_damp = def.beam_defaults->damping_constant;
4157  shock.springin = def.spring_in;
4158  shock.dampin = def.damp_in;
4159  shock.springout = def.spring_out;
4160  shock.dampout = def.damp_out;
4161  shock.sprogin = def.progress_factor_spring_in;
4162  shock.dprogin = def.progress_factor_damp_in;
4163  shock.sprogout = def.progress_factor_spring_out;
4164  shock.dprogout = def.progress_factor_damp_out;
4165 
4166  beam.shock = & shock;
4167  shock.beamid = beam_index;
4168 }
4169 
4170 void RigSpawner::ProcessShock(RigDef::Shock & def)
4171 {
4172  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
4173 
4174  if (! CheckShockLimit(1) || ! CheckBeamLimit(1))
4175  {
4176  return;
4177  }
4178 
4179  node_t & node_1 = GetNode(def.nodes[0]);
4180  node_t & node_2 = GetNode(def.nodes[1]);
4181  float short_bound = def.short_bound;
4182  float long_bound = def.long_bound;
4183  unsigned int hydro_type = BEAM_HYDRO;
4184  unsigned int shock_flags = SHOCK_FLAG_NORMAL;
4185 
4186  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.options, RigDef::Shock::OPTION_i_INVISIBLE))
4187  {
4188  BITMASK_SET_1(shock_flags, SHOCK_FLAG_INVISIBLE);
4189  hydro_type = BEAM_INVISIBLE_HYDRO;
4190  }
4191  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.options, RigDef::Shock::OPTION_L_ACTIVE_LEFT))
4192  {
4193  BITMASK_SET_0(shock_flags, SHOCK_FLAG_NORMAL); /* Not normal anymore */
4194  BITMASK_SET_1(shock_flags, SHOCK_FLAG_LACTIVE);
4195  m_rig->free_active_shock++; /* This has no array associated with it. its just to determine if there are active shocks! */
4196  }
4197  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.options, RigDef::Shock::OPTION_L_ACTIVE_LEFT))
4198  {
4199  BITMASK_SET_0(shock_flags, SHOCK_FLAG_NORMAL); /* Not normal anymore */
4200  BITMASK_SET_1(shock_flags, SHOCK_FLAG_RACTIVE);
4201  m_rig->free_active_shock++; /* This has no array associated with it. its just to determine if there are active shocks! */
4202  }
4203  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.options, RigDef::Shock::OPTION_m_METRIC))
4204  {
4205  float beam_length = node_1.AbsPosition.distance(node_2.AbsPosition);
4206  short_bound /= beam_length;
4207  long_bound /= beam_length;
4208  }
4209 
4210  int beam_index = m_rig->free_beam;
4211  beam_t & beam = AddBeam(node_1, node_2, def.beam_defaults, DEFAULT_DETACHER_GROUP);
4212  beam.shortbound = short_bound;
4213  beam.longbound = long_bound;
4214  beam.bounded = SHOCK1;
4215  beam.type = hydro_type;
4216  beam.k = def.spring_rate;
4217  beam.d = def.damping;
4218  SetBeamStrength(beam, def.beam_defaults->breaking_threshold_constant * 4.f);
4219  beam.diameter = DEFAULT_BEAM_DIAMETER;
4220 
4221  /* Length + pre-compression */
4222  CalculateBeamLength(beam);
4223  beam.L *= def.precompression;
4224  beam.refL *= def.precompression;
4225  beam.Lhydro *= def.precompression;
4226 
4227  shock_t & shock = GetFreeShock();
4228  shock.flags = shock_flags;
4229  shock.sbd_spring = def.beam_defaults->springiness;
4230  shock.sbd_damp = def.beam_defaults->damping_constant;
4231 
4232  /* Create beam visuals, but don't attach them to scene graph */
4233  /* Old parser did it like this, I don't know why ~ only_a_ptr 13-04-14 */
4234  CreateBeamVisuals(beam, beam_index, def.beam_defaults, false);
4235 
4236  beam.shock = & shock;
4237  shock.beamid = beam_index;
4238 }

4240 void RigSpawner::FetchAxisNodes(
4241  node_t* & axis_node_1,
4242  node_t* & axis_node_2,
4243  RigDef::Node::Ref const & axis_node_1_id,
4244  RigDef::Node::Ref const & axis_node_2_id
4245 )
4246 {
4247  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
4248 
4249  axis_node_1 = GetNodePointer(axis_node_1_id);
4250  axis_node_2 = GetNodePointer(axis_node_2_id);
4251 
4252  /* Enforce the "second node must have a larger Z coordinate than the first" constraint */
4253  if (axis_node_1->RelPosition.z > axis_node_2->RelPosition.z)
4254  {
4255  node_t *swap = axis_node_1;
4256  axis_node_1 = axis_node_2;
4257  axis_node_2 = swap;
4258  }
4259 }
4260 
4261 void RigSpawner::ProcessFlexBodyWheel(RigDef::FlexBodyWheel & def)
4262 {

4264 
4265  /* Check capacities */
4266  CheckNodeLimit(def.num_rays * 4);
4267  CheckBeamLimit(def.num_rays * (def.rigidity_node.IsValidAnyState()) ? 26 : 25);
4268  CheckFlexbodyLimit(1);
4269 
4270  unsigned int base_node_index = m_rig->free_node;

4275  FetchAxisNodes(axis_node_1, axis_node_2, def.nodes[0], def.nodes[1]);
4276

4278  node_t *rigidity_node = nullptr;
4279  node_t *axis_node_closest_to_rigidity_node = nullptr;
4280  if (def.rigidity_node.IsValidAnyState())
4281  {

4283  Ogre::Real distance_1 = (rigidity_node->RelPosition - axis_node_1->RelPosition).length();
4284  Ogre::Real distance_2 = (rigidity_node->RelPosition - axis_node_2->RelPosition).length();

4300

4303  rim_ray_vector = rim_ray_rotator * rim_ray_vector;

4307

4309  outer_node.id = -1; // Orig: hardcoded (addWheel2)
4310  outer_node.wheelid = m_rig->free_wheel;
4311  outer_node.friction_coef = def.node_defaults->friction;
4312  AdjustNodeBuoyancy(outer_node, def.node_defaults);
4313

4315  ray_point = axis_node_2->RelPosition + rim_ray_vector;
4316  rim_ray_vector = rim_ray_rotator * rim_ray_vector;

4325  AdjustNodeBuoyancy(inner_node, def.node_defaults);

4329  wheel.nodes[(i * 2) + 1] = & inner_node;

4334  tyre_ray_vector = tyre_ray_rotator * tyre_ray_vector;
4335 
4336  /* Tyre nodes */
4337  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < def.num_rays; i++)
4338  {

4340  float node_mass = def.mass / (4.f * def.num_rays);
4341  Ogre::Vector3 ray_point = axis_node_1->RelPosition + tyre_ray_vector;
4342  tyre_ray_vector = tyre_ray_rotator * tyre_ray_vector;

4353  AdjustNodeBuoyancy(outer_node, def.node_defaults);

4358  outer_contacter.opticontact = 0;
4359  m_rig->free_contacter++;
4360

4390  float rim_damp = def.rim_damping;
4391  float tyre_spring = def.tyre_springiness;
4392  float tyre_damp = def.tyre_damping;
4393  float tread_spring = def.beam_defaults->springiness;
4394  float tread_damp = def.beam_defaults->damping_constant;
4395  /*
4396  Calculate the point where the support beams get stiff and prevent the tire tread nodes
4397  bounce into the rim rimradius / tire radius and add 5%, this is a shortbound calc in % !
4398  */
4399  float support_beams_short_bound = 1.0f - ((def.rim_radius / def.tyre_radius) * 0.95f);
4400 
4401  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < def.num_rays; i++)
4402  {
4403  /* --- Rim --- */
4404 
4405  /* Rim axis to rim ring */
4406  unsigned int rim_outer_node_index = base_node_index + (i * 2);
4407  node_t *rim_outer_node = & m_rig->nodes[rim_outer_node_index];
4408  node_t *rim_inner_node = & m_rig->nodes[rim_outer_node_index + 1];
4409 
4410  AddWheelBeam(axis_node_1, rim_outer_node, rim_spring, rim_damp, def.beam_defaults);
4411  AddWheelBeam(axis_node_2, rim_inner_node, rim_spring, rim_damp, def.beam_defaults);
4412  AddWheelBeam(axis_node_2, rim_outer_node, rim_spring, rim_damp, def.beam_defaults);
4413  AddWheelBeam(axis_node_1, rim_inner_node, rim_spring, rim_damp, def.beam_defaults);

4417  node_t *rim_next_outer_node = & m_rig->nodes[rim_next_outer_node_index];

4421  AddWheelBeam(rim_outer_node, rim_next_outer_node, rim_spring, rim_damp, def.beam_defaults);
4422  AddWheelBeam(rim_inner_node, rim_next_inner_node, rim_spring, rim_damp, def.beam_defaults);
4423  AddWheelBeam(rim_inner_node, rim_next_outer_node, rim_spring, rim_damp, def.beam_defaults);
4424  }

4426  /* Tyre beams */
4427  /* Quick&dirty port from original SerializedRig::addWheel3() */
4428  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < def.num_rays; i++)
4429  {
4430  int rim_node_index = base_node_index + i*2;
4431  int tyre_node_index = base_node_index + i*2 + def.num_rays*2;
4432  node_t * rim_node = & m_rig->nodes[rim_node_index];
4433

4435

4437  AddWheelBeam(rim_node, & m_rig->nodes[tyre_base_index - 1], tyre_spring/2.f, tyre_damp, def.beam_defaults);
4438  AddWheelBeam(rim_node, & m_rig->nodes[tyre_base_index - 2], tyre_spring/2.f, tyre_damp, def.beam_defaults);

4442  AddWheelBeam(next_rim_node, & m_rig->nodes[tyre_node_index + 1], tyre_spring/2.f, tyre_damp, def.beam_defaults);

4446  node_t * tyre_node = & m_rig->nodes[index];
4447  AddWheelBeam(next_rim_node, tyre_node, tyre_spring/2.f, tyre_damp, def.beam_defaults);
4448  }
4449 
4450  //reinforcement (tire tread)
4451  {
4452  // Very messy port :(
4453  // Aliases
4454  int rimnode = rim_node_index;
4455  int rays = def.num_rays;
4456 
4457  AddWheelBeam(&m_rig->nodes[rimnode+rays*2], &m_rig->nodes[base_node_index+i*2+1+rays*2], tread_spring, tread_damp, def.beam_defaults);
4458  AddWheelBeam(&m_rig->nodes[rimnode+rays*2], &m_rig->nodes[base_node_index+((i+1)%rays)*2+rays*2], tread_spring, tread_damp, def.beam_defaults);
4459  AddWheelBeam(&m_rig->nodes[base_node_index+i*2+1+rays*2], &m_rig->nodes[base_node_index+((i+1)%rays)*2+1+rays*2], tread_spring, tread_damp, def.beam_defaults);
4460  AddWheelBeam(&m_rig->nodes[rimnode+1+rays*2], &m_rig->nodes[base_node_index+((i+1)%rays)*2+rays*2], tread_spring, tread_damp, def.beam_defaults);
4461 
4462  if (rigidity_node != nullptr)
4463  {
4464 
4465  if (axis_node_closest_to_rigidity_node == axis_node_1)
4466  {
4467  axis_node_closest_to_rigidity_node = & m_rig->nodes[base_node_index+i*2+rays*2];
4468  } else
4469  {
4470  axis_node_closest_to_rigidity_node = & m_rig->nodes[base_node_index+i*2+1+rays*2];
4471  };
4472  unsigned int beam_index = AddWheelBeam(rigidity_node, axis_node_closest_to_rigidity_node, tyre_spring, tyre_damp, def.beam_defaults);
4473  GetBeam(beam_index).type = BEAM_VIRTUAL;
4474  }
4475  }
4476  }
4477 
4478  //calculate the point where the support beams get stiff and prevent the tire tread nodes bounce into the rim rimradius / tire radius and add 5%, this is a shortbound calc in % !
4479  float length = 1.0f - ((def.rim_radius / def.tyre_radius) * 0.95f);
4480  float ropespring = def.rim_springiness;
4481 
4482  if (ropespring <= DEFAULT_SPRING)
4483  ropespring = DEFAULT_SPRING;
4484 
4485  for (unsigned int i=0; i<def.num_rays; i++)
4486  {
4487  //tiretread anti collapse reinforcements, using precalced support beams
4488  unsigned int tirenode = base_node_index + i*2 + def.num_rays*2;
4489  unsigned int beam_index;
4490 
4491  beam_index = AddWheelBeam(axis_node_1, &m_rig->nodes[tirenode], tyre_spring/2.f, tyre_damp, def.beam_defaults);
4492  GetBeam(beam_index).shortbound = length;
4493  GetBeam(beam_index).longbound = 0.f;
4494  GetBeam(beam_index).bounded = SHOCK1;
4495 
4496  beam_index = AddWheelBeam(axis_node_2, &m_rig->nodes[tirenode + 1], tyre_spring/2.f, tyre_damp, def.beam_defaults);
4497  GetBeam(beam_index).shortbound = length;
4498  GetBeam(beam_index).longbound = 0.f;
4499  GetBeam(beam_index).bounded = SHOCK1;
4500  }
4501 
4502  /* Wheel object */
4503  wheel.braked = def.braking;
4504  wheel.propulsed = def.propulsion;
4505  wheel.nbnodes = 2 * def.num_rays;
4506  wheel.refnode0 = axis_node_1;
4507  wheel.refnode1 = axis_node_2;
4508  wheel.radius = def.tyre_radius;
4509  wheel.arm = GetNodePointer(def.reference_arm_node);
4510 
4511  if (def.propulsion != RigDef::Wheels::PROPULSION_NONE)
4512  {
4513  /* for inter-differential locking */
4514  m_rig->proped_wheels++;
4515  m_rig->proppairs[m_rig->proped_wheels] = m_rig->free_wheel;
4516  m_rig->propwheelcount++;
4517  }
4518  if (def.braking != RigDef::Wheels::BRAKING_NO)
4519  {
4520  m_rig->braked_wheels++;
4521  }
4522 
4523  /* Find near attach */
4524  Ogre::Real length_1 = (axis_node_1->RelPosition - wheel.arm->RelPosition).length();
4525  Ogre::Real length_2 = (axis_node_2->RelPosition - wheel.arm->RelPosition).length();
4526  wheel.near_attach = (length_1 < length_2) ? axis_node_1 : axis_node_2;
4527 
4528  /* Create visuals */
4529  BuildMeshWheelVisuals(

4532  axis_node_1->pos,
4533  axis_node_2->pos,

4537  def.rim_radius,
4538  def.side != RigDef::MeshWheel::SIDE_RIGHT
4539  );
4540

4544

4568  m_rig->free_wheel++;

4571 void RigSpawner::ProcessMeshWheel(RigDef::MeshWheel & meshwheel_def)
4572 {
4573  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
4574 
4575  unsigned int base_node_index = m_rig->free_node;

4577  node_t *axis_node_2 = GetNodePointer(meshwheel_def.nodes[1]);
4578 
4579  /* Enforce the "second node must have a larger Z coordinate than the first" constraint */
4580  if (axis_node_1->RelPosition.z > axis_node_2->RelPosition.z)
4581  {
4582  node_t *swap = axis_node_1;
4583  axis_node_1 = axis_node_2;
4584  axis_node_2 = swap;
4585  }

4593  meshwheel_def.num_rays * 8,

4595  meshwheel_def.propulsion,
4596  meshwheel_def.braking,
4597  meshwheel_def.node_defaults,
4598  meshwheel_def.mass
4599  );

4601  BuildWheelBeams(

4604  axis_node_1,
4605  axis_node_2,
4606  meshwheel_def.spring, /* Tyre */
4607  meshwheel_def.damping, /* Tyre */

4609  meshwheel_def.damping, /* Rim */
4610  meshwheel_def.beam_defaults,

4612  );
4613 
4614  BuildMeshWheelVisuals(

4617  axis_node_1->pos,
4618  axis_node_2->pos,
4619  meshwheel_def.num_rays,

4624  );

4697 
4698 void RigSpawner::BuildMeshWheelVisuals(
4699  unsigned int wheel_index,
4700  unsigned int base_node_index,
4701  unsigned int axis_node_1_index,
4702  unsigned int axis_node_2_index,
4703  unsigned int num_rays,
4704  Ogre::String mesh_name,
4705  Ogre::String material_name,
4706  float rim_radius,
4707  bool rim_reverse
4708 )
4709 {
4710  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
4711 
4712  std::stringstream wheel_name;
4713  wheel_name << "wheel-" << m_rig->truckname << "-" << wheel_index;
4714  std::stringstream entity_name;
4715  entity_name << "wheelobj-" << m_rig->truckname << "-" << wheel_index;
4716 
4717  m_rig->vwheels[wheel_index].fm = new FlexMeshWheel(
4718  wheel_name.str(),
4719  m_rig->nodes,
4720  axis_node_1_index,
4721  axis_node_2_index,
4722  base_node_index,
4723  num_rays,
4724  mesh_name,
4725  material_name,
4726  rim_radius,
4727  rim_reverse,
4728  m_rig->materialFunctionMapper,
4729  m_rig->usedSkin,
4730  m_rig->materialReplacer
4731  );
4732  m_rig->vwheels[wheel_index].meshwheel = true;
4733 
4734  try
4735  {
4736  m_rig->vwheels[wheel_index].cnode = gEnv->sceneManager->getRootSceneNode()->createChildSceneNode();
4737  Ogre::Entity *ec = gEnv->sceneManager->createEntity(entity_name.str(), wheel_name.str());
4738  if (ec)
4739  {
4740  m_rig->deletion_Entities.emplace_back(ec);
4741  m_rig->vwheels[wheel_index].cnode->attachObject(ec);
4742  }
4743 
4744  MaterialFunctionMapper::replaceSimpleMeshMaterials(ec, Ogre::ColourValue(0, 0.5, 0.5));
4745  if (m_rig->materialFunctionMapper != nullptr)
4746  {
4747  m_rig->materialFunctionMapper->replaceMeshMaterials(ec);
4748  }
4749  if (m_rig->materialReplacer != nullptr)
4750  {
4751  m_rig->materialReplacer->replaceMeshMaterials(ec);
4752  }
4753  if (m_rig->usedSkin != nullptr)
4754  {
4755  m_rig->usedSkin->replaceMeshMaterials(ec);
4756  }
4757  }
4758  catch(...)
4759  {
4760  std::stringstream msg;
4761  msg << "Error loading mesh: " << mesh_name;
4762  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_ERROR, msg.str());
4763  }
4764 }
4765 
4766 unsigned int RigSpawner::BuildWheelObjectAndNodes(
4767  unsigned int num_rays,
4768  node_t *axis_node_1,
4769  node_t *axis_node_2,
4770  node_t *reference_arm_node,
4771  unsigned int reserve_nodes,
4772  unsigned int reserve_beams,
4773  float wheel_radius,
4774  RigDef::Wheels::Propulsion propulsion,
4775  RigDef::Wheels::Braking braking,
4776  boost::shared_ptr<RigDef::NodeDefaults> node_defaults,
4777  float wheel_mass,
4778  bool set_param_iswheel, /* Default: true */
4779  float wheel_width /* Default: -1.f */
4780 )
4781 {
4782  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
4783 
4784  /* Check capacity */
4785  CheckNodeLimit(reserve_nodes);
4786  CheckBeamLimit(reserve_beams);
4787 
4788  wheel_t & wheel = m_rig->wheels[m_rig->free_wheel];
4789 
4790  /* Axis */
4791  Ogre::Vector3 axis_vector = axis_node_2->RelPosition - axis_node_1->RelPosition;
4792  float axis_length = axis_vector.length();
4793  axis_vector.normalise();
4794 
4795  /* Wheel object */
4796  wheel.braked = braking;
4797  wheel.propulsed = propulsion;
4798  wheel.nbnodes = 2 * num_rays;
4799  wheel.refnode0 = axis_node_1;
4800  wheel.refnode1 = axis_node_2;
4801  wheel.radius = wheel_radius;
4802  wheel.width = (wheel_width < 0) ? axis_length : wheel_width;
4803  wheel.arm = reference_arm_node;
4804 
4805  /* Find near attach */
4806  Ogre::Real length_1 = (axis_node_1->RelPosition - wheel.arm->RelPosition).length();
4807  Ogre::Real length_2 = (axis_node_2->RelPosition - wheel.arm->RelPosition).length();
4808  wheel.near_attach = (length_1 < length_2) ? axis_node_1 : axis_node_2;
4809 
4810  if (propulsion != RigDef::Wheels::PROPULSION_NONE)
4811  {
4812  m_rig->propwheelcount++;
4813  /* for inter-differential locking */
4814  m_rig->proped_wheels++;
4815  m_rig->proppairs[m_rig->proped_wheels] = m_rig->free_wheel;
4816  }
4817  if (braking != RigDef::Wheels::BRAKING_NO)
4818  {
4819  m_rig->braked_wheels++;
4820  }
4821 
4822  /* Nodes */
4823  Ogre::Vector3 ray_vector = axis_vector.perpendicular() * wheel_radius;
4824  Ogre::Quaternion ray_rotator = Ogre::Quaternion(Ogre::Degree(-360.0 / (num_rays * 2)), axis_vector);
4825 
4826 #ifdef DEBUG_TRUCKPARSER2013
4827  // TRUCK PARSER 2013 DEBUG
4828  std::stringstream msg;
4829  msg << "\nDBG RigSpawner::BuildWheelObjectAndNodes()\nDBG nodebase:" << m_rig->free_node <<", axis-node-0:"<<axis_node_1->pos <<", axis-node-1:"<<axis_node_2->pos<<"\n";
4830  msg << "DBG ==== Adding nodes ====";
4831  // END
4832 #endif
4833 
4834  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < num_rays; i++)
4835  {
4836  /* Outer ring */
4837  Ogre::Vector3 ray_point = axis_node_1->RelPosition + ray_vector;
4838  ray_vector = ray_rotator * ray_vector;
4839 
4840  node_t & outer_node = GetFreeNode();
4841  InitNode(outer_node, ray_point, node_defaults);
4842  outer_node.mass = wheel_mass / (2.f * num_rays);
4843  outer_node.iswheel = (set_param_iswheel) ? (m_rig->free_wheel * 2) + 1 : 0;
4844  outer_node.id = -1; // Orig: hardcoded (BTS_WHEELS)
4845  outer_node.wheelid = m_rig->free_wheel;
4846  AdjustNodeBuoyancy(outer_node, node_defaults);
4847 
4848  contacter_t & outer_contacter = m_rig->contacters[m_rig->free_contacter];
4849  outer_contacter.nodeid = outer_node.pos; /* Node index */
4850  outer_contacter.contacted = 0;
4851  outer_contacter.opticontact = 0;
4852  m_rig->free_contacter++;
4853 
4854  /* Inner ring */
4855  ray_point = axis_node_2->RelPosition + ray_vector;
4856  ray_vector = ray_rotator * ray_vector;
4857 
4858  node_t & inner_node = GetFreeNode();
4859  InitNode(inner_node, ray_point, node_defaults);
4860  inner_node.mass = wheel_mass / (2.f * num_rays);
4861  inner_node.iswheel = (set_param_iswheel) ? (m_rig->free_wheel * 2) + 2 : 0;
4862  inner_node.id = -1; // Orig: hardcoded (BTS_WHEELS)
4863  inner_node.wheelid = m_rig->free_wheel;
4864  AdjustNodeBuoyancy(inner_node, node_defaults);
4865 
4866  contacter_t & contacter = m_rig->contacters[m_rig->free_contacter];
4867  contacter.nodeid = inner_node.pos; /* Node index */
4868  contacter.contacted = 0;
4869  contacter.opticontact = 0;
4870  m_rig->free_contacter++;
4871 
4872  /* Wheel object */
4873  wheel.nodes[i * 2] = & outer_node;
4874  wheel.nodes[(i * 2) + 1] = & inner_node;
4875 
4876 #ifdef DEBUG_TRUCKPARSER2013
4877  // TRUCK PARSER 2013 DEBUG
4878  int modifier = 0;
4879  msg << "\nDBG\tN1: index=" << outer_node.pos + modifier <<", wheelid=" << outer_node.wheelid << ", iswheel=" << outer_node.iswheel
4880  <<", X=" << outer_node.AbsPosition.x <<", Y=" << outer_node.AbsPosition.y <<", Z=" << outer_node.AbsPosition.z << std::endl
4881  << "DBG\tN2: index=" << inner_node.pos + modifier <<", wheelid=" << inner_node.wheelid << ", iswheel=" << inner_node.iswheel
4882  <<", X=" << inner_node.AbsPosition.x <<", Y=" << inner_node.AbsPosition.y <<", Z=" << inner_node.AbsPosition.z;
4883  // END
4884 #endif
4885  }
4886 
4887 #ifdef DEBUG_TRUCKPARSER2013
4888  // TRUCK PARSER 2013 DEBUG
4889  LOG(msg.str());
4890  // END
4891 #endif
4892 
4893  /* Advance */
4894  unsigned int wheel_index = m_rig->free_wheel;
4895  m_rig->free_wheel++;
4896  return wheel_index;
4897 }

4899 void RigSpawner::AdjustNodeBuoyancy(node_t & node, RigDef::Node & node_def, boost::shared_ptr<RigDef::NodeDefaults> defaults)
4900 {

4902 
4903  unsigned int options = (defaults->options | node_def.options); // Merge flags
4904  node.buoyancy = BITMASK_IS_1(options, RigDef::Node::OPTION_b_EXTRA_BUOYANCY) ? 10000.f : m_rig->truckmass/15.f;
4905 }

4914 int RigSpawner::FindLowestNodeInRig()
4915 {
4916  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
4917 
4918  int lowest_node_index = 0;
4919  float lowest_y = m_rig->nodes[0].AbsPosition.y;
4920 
4921  for (int i = 0; i < m_rig->free_node; i++)
4922  {
4923  float y = m_rig->nodes[i].AbsPosition.y;
4924  if (y < lowest_y)
4925  {
4926  lowest_y = y;
4927  lowest_node_index = i;
4928  }
4929  }
4930 
4931  return lowest_node_index;
4932 }
4933 
4934 void RigSpawner::BuildWheelBeams(
4935  unsigned int num_rays,
4936  unsigned int base_node_index,
4937  node_t *axis_node_1,
4938  node_t *axis_node_2,
4939  float tyre_spring,
4940  float tyre_damping,
4941  float rim_spring,
4942  float rim_damping,
4943  boost::shared_ptr<RigDef::BeamDefaults> beam_defaults,
4944  RigDef::Node::Ref const & rigidity_node_id,
4945  float max_extension // = 0.f
4946 )
4947 {
4948  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
4949 
4950 #ifdef DEBUG_TRUCKPARSER2013
4951  // DEBUG
4952  std::stringstream msg;
4953  msg << "==== BEAMS ====";
4954  // END DEBUG
4955 #endif
4956 
4957  /* Find out where to connect rigidity node */
4958  bool rigidity_beam_side_1 = false;
4959  node_t *rigidity_node = nullptr;
4960  if (rigidity_node_id.IsValidAnyState())
4961  {
4962  rigidity_node = GetNodePointerOrThrow(rigidity_node_id);
4963  float distance_1 = rigidity_node->RelPosition.distance(axis_node_1->RelPosition);
4964  float distance_2 = rigidity_node->RelPosition.distance(axis_node_2->RelPosition);
4965  rigidity_beam_side_1 = distance_1 < distance_2;
4966  }
4967 
4968  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < num_rays; i++)
4969  {
4970  /* Bounded */
4971  unsigned int outer_ring_node_index = base_node_index + (i * 2);
4972  node_t *outer_ring_node = & m_rig->nodes[outer_ring_node_index];
4973  node_t *inner_ring_node = & m_rig->nodes[outer_ring_node_index + 1];
4974 
4975  AddWheelBeam(axis_node_1, outer_ring_node, tyre_spring, tyre_damping, beam_defaults, 0.66f, max_extension);
4976  AddWheelBeam(axis_node_2, inner_ring_node, tyre_spring, tyre_damping, beam_defaults, 0.66f, max_extension);
4977  AddWheelBeam(axis_node_2, outer_ring_node, tyre_spring, tyre_damping, beam_defaults);
4978  AddWheelBeam(axis_node_1, inner_ring_node, tyre_spring, tyre_damping, beam_defaults);
4979 
4980  /* Reinforcement */
4981  unsigned int next_outer_ring_node_index = base_node_index + (((i + 1) % num_rays) * 2);
4982  node_t *next_outer_ring_node = & m_rig->nodes[next_outer_ring_node_index];
4983  node_t *next_inner_ring_node = & m_rig->nodes[next_outer_ring_node_index + 1];
4984 
4985  AddWheelBeam(outer_ring_node, inner_ring_node, rim_spring, rim_damping, beam_defaults);
4986  AddWheelBeam(outer_ring_node, next_outer_ring_node, rim_spring, rim_damping, beam_defaults);
4987  AddWheelBeam(inner_ring_node, next_inner_ring_node, rim_spring, rim_damping, beam_defaults);
4988  AddWheelBeam(inner_ring_node, next_outer_ring_node, rim_spring, rim_damping, beam_defaults);
4989 
4990 #ifdef DEBUG_TRUCKPARSER2013
4991  // TRUCK PARSER 2013 DEBUG
4992  int modifier = 0;
4993  msg<<"\nDBG\tBounded: ";
4994  msg<<"["<<axis_node_1->pos + modifier<<" "<<outer_ring_node->pos + modifier<<"] ";
4995  msg<<"["<<axis_node_2->pos + modifier<<" "<<inner_ring_node->pos + modifier<<"] ";
4996  msg<<"["<<axis_node_2->pos + modifier<<" "<<outer_ring_node->pos + modifier<<"] ";
4997  msg<<"["<<axis_node_1->pos + modifier<<" "<<inner_ring_node->pos + modifier<<"]";
4998  //reinforcement
4999  msg<<"\nDBG\tReinforcement: ";
5000  msg<<"["<<outer_ring_node->pos + modifier<<" "<<inner_ring_node->pos + modifier<<"] ";
5001  msg<<"["<<outer_ring_node->pos + modifier<<" "<<next_outer_ring_node->pos + modifier<<"] ";
5002  msg<<"["<<inner_ring_node->pos + modifier<<" "<<next_inner_ring_node->pos + modifier<<"] ";
5003  msg<<"["<<inner_ring_node->pos + modifier<<" "<<next_outer_ring_node->pos + modifier<<"] ";
5004  // END
5005 #endif
5006 
5007  /* Rigidity beams */
5008  if (rigidity_node != nullptr)
5009  {
5010  node_t *target_node = (rigidity_beam_side_1) ? outer_ring_node : inner_ring_node;
5011  unsigned int beam_index = AddWheelBeam(rigidity_node, target_node, tyre_spring, tyre_damping, beam_defaults, -1.f, -1.f, BEAM_VIRTUAL);
5012  m_rig->beams[beam_index].type = BEAM_VIRTUAL;
5013 
5014 #ifdef DEBUG_TRUCKPARSER2013
5015  // DEBUG
5016  msg<<"\nDBG\tRigidityBeam: ["<<rigidity_node->pos + modifier<<" "<<target_node->pos + modifier<<"] ";
5017  msg<<((rigidity_beam_side_1) ? "(outer)" : "(inner)");
5018  // END
5019 #endif
5020  }
5021  }
5022 #ifdef DEBUG_TRUCKPARSER2013
5023  // TRUCK PARSER 2013 DEBUG
5024  LOG(msg.str());
5025  // END
5026 #endif
5027 }

5029 unsigned int RigSpawner::AddWheel(RigDef::Wheel & wheel_def)
5030 {
5031  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
5032 
5033  unsigned int base_node_index = m_rig->free_node;
5034  node_t *axis_node_1 = GetNodePointer(wheel_def.nodes[0]);
5035  node_t *axis_node_2 = GetNodePointer(wheel_def.nodes[1]);
5036 
5037  if (axis_node_1 == nullptr || axis_node_2 == nullptr)
5038  {
5039  std::stringstream msg;
5040  msg << "Error creating 'wheel': Some axis nodes were not found";
5041  msg << " (Node1: " << wheel_def.nodes[0].ToString() << " => " << (axis_node_1 == nullptr) ? "NOT FOUND)" : "found)";
5042  msg << " (Node2: " << wheel_def.nodes[1].ToString() << " => " << (axis_node_2 == nullptr) ? "NOT FOUND)" : "found)";
5043  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_ERROR, msg.str());
5044  return -1;
5045  }
5046 
5047  /* Enforce the "second node must have a larger Z coordinate than the first" constraint */
5048  if (axis_node_1->RelPosition.z > axis_node_2->RelPosition.z)
5049  {
5050  node_t *swap = axis_node_1;
5051  axis_node_1 = axis_node_2;
5052  axis_node_2 = swap;
5053  }
5054 
5055  unsigned int wheel_index = BuildWheelObjectAndNodes(
5056  wheel_def.num_rays,
5057  axis_node_1,
5058  axis_node_2,
5059  GetNodePointer(wheel_def.reference_arm_node),
5060  wheel_def.num_rays * 2,
5061  wheel_def.num_rays * 8,
5062  wheel_def.radius,
5063  wheel_def.propulsion,
5064  wheel_def.braking,
5065  wheel_def.node_defaults,
5066  wheel_def.mass,
5067  true,
5068  -1.f // Set width to axis length (width in definition is ignored)
5069  );
5070 
5071  BuildWheelBeams(
5072  wheel_def.num_rays,
5073  base_node_index,
5074  axis_node_1,
5075  axis_node_2,
5076  wheel_def.springiness, /* Tyre */
5077  wheel_def.damping, /* Tyre */
5078  wheel_def.springiness, /* Rim */
5079  wheel_def.damping, /* Rim */
5080  wheel_def.beam_defaults,
5081  wheel_def.rigidity_node
5082  );
5083 
5084  CreateWheelVisuals(wheel_index, wheel_def, base_node_index);
5085 
5086  return wheel_index;
5087 }

5223 unsigned int RigSpawner::AddWheel2(RigDef::Wheel2 & wheel_2_def)

5248  {
5249  node_t *swap = axis_node_1;
5250  axis_node_1 = axis_node_2;
5251  axis_node_2 = swap;
5252  }
5253 
5254  /* Rigidity node */
5255  node_t *axis_node_closest_to_rigidity_node = nullptr;
5256  if (wheel_2_def.rigidity_node.IsValidAnyState())
5257  {
5258  node_t & rigidity_node = GetNode(wheel_2_def.rigidity_node);
5259  Ogre::Real distance_1 = (rigidity_node.RelPosition - axis_node_1->RelPosition).length();
5260  Ogre::Real distance_2 = (rigidity_node.RelPosition - axis_node_2->RelPosition).length();
5261  axis_node_closest_to_rigidity_node = ((distance_1 < distance_2)) ? axis_node_1 : axis_node_2;
5262  }
5263 
5264  /* Node&beam generation */
5265  Ogre::Vector3 axis_vector = axis_node_2->RelPosition - axis_node_1->RelPosition;
5266  axis_vector.normalise();
5267  Ogre::Vector3 rim_ray_vector = Ogre::Vector3(0, wheel_2_def.rim_radius, 0);
5268  Ogre::Quaternion rim_ray_rotator = Ogre::Quaternion(Ogre::Degree(-360.f / wheel_2_def.num_rays), axis_vector);
5269 
5270  /* Width */
5271  wheel.width = axis_vector.length(); /* wheel_def.width is ignored. */
5272 
5273  /* Rim nodes */
5274  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < wheel_2_def.num_rays; i++)
5275  {
5276  float node_mass = wheel_2_def.mass / (4.f * wheel_2_def.num_rays);
5277 
5278  /* Outer ring */
5279  Ogre::Vector3 ray_point = axis_node_1->RelPosition + rim_ray_vector;
5280 
5281  node_t & outer_node = GetFreeNode();
5282  InitNode(outer_node, ray_point, wheel_2_def.node_defaults);
5283  outer_node.mass = node_mass;
5284  outer_node.iswheel = (m_rig->free_wheel * 2) + 1;
5285  outer_node.id = -1; // Orig: hardcoded (addWheel2)
5286  outer_node.wheelid = m_rig->free_wheel;
5287 
5288  /* Inner ring */
5289  ray_point = axis_node_2->RelPosition + rim_ray_vector;
5290 
5291  node_t & inner_node = GetFreeNode();
5292  InitNode(inner_node, ray_point, wheel_2_def.node_defaults);
5293  inner_node.mass = node_mass;
5294  inner_node.iswheel = (m_rig->free_wheel * 2) + 2;
5295  inner_node.id = -1; // Orig: hardcoded (addWheel2)
5296  inner_node.wheelid = m_rig->free_wheel;
5297 
5298  /* Wheel object */
5299  wheel.nodes[i * 2] = & outer_node;
5300  wheel.nodes[(i * 2) + 1] = & inner_node;
5301 
5302  rim_ray_vector = rim_ray_rotator * rim_ray_vector;
5303  }
5304 
5305  Ogre::Vector3 tyre_ray_vector = Ogre::Vector3(0, wheel_2_def.tyre_radius, 0);
5306  Ogre::Quaternion tyre_ray_rotator = Ogre::Quaternion(Ogre::Degree(-180.f / wheel_2_def.num_rays), axis_vector);
5307  tyre_ray_vector = tyre_ray_rotator * tyre_ray_vector;
5308 
5309  /* Tyre nodes */
5310  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < wheel_2_def.num_rays; i++)
5311  {
5312  /* Outer ring */
5313  Ogre::Vector3 ray_point = axis_node_1->RelPosition + tyre_ray_vector;
5314 
5315  node_t & outer_node = GetFreeNode();
5316  InitNode(outer_node, ray_point);
5317  outer_node.mass = (0.67f * wheel_2_def.mass) / (2.f * wheel_2_def.num_rays);
5318  outer_node.iswheel = (m_rig->free_wheel * 2) + 1;
5319  outer_node.id = -1; // Orig: hardcoded (addWheel2)
5320  outer_node.wheelid = m_rig->free_wheel;
5321  outer_node.friction_coef = wheel.width * WHEEL_FRICTION_COEF;
5322  outer_node.volume_coef = wheel_2_def.node_defaults->volume;
5323  outer_node.surface_coef = wheel_2_def.node_defaults->surface;
5324 
5325  contacter_t & contacter = m_rig->contacters[m_rig->free_contacter];
5326  contacter.nodeid = outer_node.pos; /* Node index */
5327  contacter.contacted = 0;
5328  contacter.opticontact = 0;
5329  m_rig->free_contacter++;
5330 
5331  /* Inner ring */
5332  ray_point = axis_node_2->RelPosition + tyre_ray_vector;
5333 
5334  node_t & inner_node = GetFreeNode();
5335  InitNode(inner_node, ray_point);
5336  inner_node.mass = (0.33f * wheel_2_def.mass) / (2.f * wheel_2_def.num_rays);
5337  inner_node.iswheel = (m_rig->free_wheel * 2) + 2;
5338  inner_node.id = -1; // Orig: hardcoded (addWheel2)
5339  inner_node.wheelid = m_rig->free_wheel;
5340  inner_node.friction_coef = wheel.width * WHEEL_FRICTION_COEF;
5341  inner_node.volume_coef = wheel_2_def.node_defaults->volume;
5342  inner_node.surface_coef = wheel_2_def.node_defaults->surface;
5343 
5344  contacter_t & inner_contacter = m_rig->contacters[m_rig->free_contacter];
5345  inner_contacter.nodeid = inner_node.pos; /* Node index */
5346  inner_contacter.contacted = 0;
5347  inner_contacter.opticontact = 0;
5348  m_rig->free_contacter++;
5349 
5350  /* Wheel object */
5351  wheel.nodes[i * 2] = & outer_node;
5352  wheel.nodes[(i * 2) + 1] = & inner_node;
5353 
5354  tyre_ray_vector = rim_ray_rotator * tyre_ray_vector; // This is OK
5355  }
5356 
5357  /* Beams */
5358  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < wheel_2_def.num_rays; i++)
5359  {
5360  /* --- Rim --- */
5361 
5362  /* Bounded */
5363  unsigned int rim_outer_node_index = base_node_index + (i * 2);
5364  node_t *rim_outer_node = & m_rig->nodes[rim_outer_node_index];
5365  node_t *rim_inner_node = & m_rig->nodes[rim_outer_node_index + 1];
5366 
5367  unsigned int beam_index;
5368  beam_index = AddWheelRimBeam(wheel_2_def, axis_node_1, rim_outer_node);
5369  GetBeam(beam_index).shortbound = 0.66;
5370  beam_index = AddWheelRimBeam(wheel_2_def, axis_node_2, rim_inner_node);
5371  GetBeam(beam_index).shortbound = 0.66;
5372  AddWheelRimBeam(wheel_2_def, axis_node_2, rim_outer_node);
5373  AddWheelRimBeam(wheel_2_def, axis_node_1, rim_inner_node);
5374 
5375  /* Reinforcement */
5376  unsigned int rim_next_outer_node_index = base_node_index + (((i + 1) % wheel_2_def.num_rays) * 2);
5377  node_t *rim_next_outer_node = & m_rig->nodes[rim_next_outer_node_index];
5378  node_t *rim_next_inner_node = & m_rig->nodes[rim_next_outer_node_index + 1];
5379 
5380  AddWheelRimBeam(wheel_2_def, axis_node_1, rim_outer_node);
5381  AddWheelRimBeam(wheel_2_def, rim_outer_node, rim_inner_node);
5382  AddWheelRimBeam(wheel_2_def, rim_outer_node, rim_next_outer_node);
5383  AddWheelRimBeam(wheel_2_def, rim_inner_node, rim_next_inner_node);
5384  AddWheelRimBeam(wheel_2_def, rim_outer_node, rim_next_inner_node);
5385  AddWheelRimBeam(wheel_2_def, rim_inner_node, rim_next_outer_node);
5386  if (axis_node_closest_to_rigidity_node != nullptr)
5387  {
5388  beam_t & beam = GetFreeBeam();
5389  InitBeam(beam, GetNodePointer(wheel_2_def.rigidity_node), axis_node_closest_to_rigidity_node);
5390  beam.type = BEAM_VIRTUAL;
5391  beam.k = wheel_2_def.rim_springiness;
5392  beam.d = wheel_2_def.rim_damping;
5393  SetBeamStrength(beam, wheel_2_def.beam_defaults->breaking_threshold_constant);
5394  }
5395 
5396  /* --- Tyre --- */
5397 
5398  unsigned int tyre_node_index = rim_outer_node_index + (2 * wheel_2_def.num_rays);
5399  node_t *tyre_outer_node = & m_rig->nodes[tyre_node_index];
5400  node_t *tyre_inner_node = & m_rig->nodes[tyre_node_index + 1];
5401  unsigned int tyre_next_node_index = rim_next_outer_node_index + (2 * wheel_2_def.num_rays);
5402  node_t *tyre_next_outer_node = & m_rig->nodes[tyre_next_node_index];
5403  node_t *tyre_next_inner_node = & m_rig->nodes[tyre_next_node_index + 1];
5404 
5405  /* Tyre band */
5406  AddTyreBeam(wheel_2_def, tyre_outer_node, tyre_next_outer_node);
5407  AddTyreBeam(wheel_2_def, tyre_outer_node, tyre_next_inner_node);
5408  AddTyreBeam(wheel_2_def, tyre_inner_node, tyre_next_outer_node);
5409  AddTyreBeam(wheel_2_def, tyre_inner_node, tyre_next_inner_node);
5410  /* Tyre sidewalls */
5411  AddTyreBeam(wheel_2_def, tyre_outer_node, rim_outer_node);
5412  AddTyreBeam(wheel_2_def, tyre_outer_node, rim_next_outer_node);
5413  AddTyreBeam(wheel_2_def, tyre_inner_node, rim_inner_node);
5414  AddTyreBeam(wheel_2_def, tyre_inner_node, rim_next_inner_node);
5415  /* Reinforcement */
5416  AddTyreBeam(wheel_2_def, tyre_outer_node, rim_inner_node);
5417  AddTyreBeam(wheel_2_def, tyre_outer_node, rim_next_inner_node);
5418  AddTyreBeam(wheel_2_def, tyre_inner_node, rim_outer_node);
5419  AddTyreBeam(wheel_2_def, tyre_inner_node, rim_next_outer_node);
5420  /* Backpressure, bounded */
5421  AddTyreBeam(wheel_2_def, axis_node_1, tyre_outer_node);
5422  AddTyreBeam(wheel_2_def, axis_node_2, tyre_inner_node);
5423  }
5424 
5425  /* Wheel object */
5426  wheel.braked = wheel_2_def.braking;
5427  wheel.propulsed = wheel_2_def.propulsion;
5428  wheel.nbnodes = 2 * wheel_2_def.num_rays;
5429  wheel.refnode0 = axis_node_1;
5430  wheel.refnode1 = axis_node_2;
5431  wheel.radius = wheel_2_def.rim_radius;
5432  wheel.arm = GetNodePointer(wheel_2_def.reference_arm_node);
5433 
5434  if (wheel_2_def.propulsion != RigDef::Wheels::PROPULSION_NONE)
5435  {
5436  /* for inter-differential locking */
5437  m_rig->proped_wheels++;
5438  m_rig->proppairs[m_rig->proped_wheels] = m_rig->free_wheel;
5439  }
5440  if (wheel_2_def.braking != RigDef::Wheels::BRAKING_NO)
5441  {
5442  m_rig->braked_wheels++;
5443  }
5444 
5445  /* Find near attach */
5446  Ogre::Real length_1 = (axis_node_1->RelPosition - wheel.arm->RelPosition).length();
5447  Ogre::Real length_2 = (axis_node_2->RelPosition - wheel.arm->RelPosition).length();
5448  wheel.near_attach = (length_1 < length_2) ? axis_node_1 : axis_node_2;
5449 
5450  /* Advance */
5451  unsigned int wheel_index = m_rig->free_wheel;
5452  m_rig->free_wheel++;
5453  return wheel_index;
5454 }

5485 void RigSpawner::CreateWheelVisuals(
5486  unsigned int wheel_index,
5487  unsigned int node_base_index,
5488  unsigned int num_rays,
5489  Ogre::String const & rim_material_name,
5490  Ogre::String const & band_material_name,
5491  bool separate_rim,
5492  float rim_ratio
5493 )
5494 {
5495  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
5496 
5497  wheel_t & wheel = m_rig->wheels[wheel_index];
5498  vwheel_t & visual_wheel = m_rig->vwheels[wheel_index];
5499 
5500  std::stringstream wheel_mesh_name;
5501  wheel_mesh_name << "wheel-" << m_rig->truckname << "-" << wheel_index;
5502  std::stringstream wheel_name_i;
5503  wheel_name_i << "wheelobj-" << m_rig->truckname << "-" << wheel_index;
5504 
5505  visual_wheel.meshwheel = false;
5506  visual_wheel.fm = new FlexMesh(
5507  wheel_mesh_name.str(),
5508  m_rig->nodes,
5509  wheel.refnode0->pos,
5510  wheel.refnode1->pos,
5511  node_base_index,
5512  num_rays,
5513  rim_material_name,
5514  band_material_name,
5515  separate_rim,
5516  rim_ratio
5517  );
5518 
5519  try
5520  {
5521  Ogre::Entity *ec = gEnv->sceneManager->createEntity(wheel_name_i.str(), wheel_mesh_name.str());
5522  MaterialFunctionMapper::replaceSimpleMeshMaterials(ec, Ogre::ColourValue(0, 0.5, 0.5));
5523  if (m_rig->materialFunctionMapper != nullptr)
5524  {
5525  m_rig->materialFunctionMapper->replaceMeshMaterials(ec);
5526  }
5527  if (m_rig->materialReplacer != nullptr)
5528  {
5529  m_rig->materialReplacer->replaceMeshMaterials(ec);
5530  }
5531  if (m_rig->usedSkin != nullptr)
5532  {
5533  m_rig->usedSkin->replaceMeshMaterials(ec);
5534  }
5535  visual_wheel.cnode = gEnv->sceneManager->getRootSceneNode()->createChildSceneNode();
5536  m_rig->deletion_Entities.emplace_back(ec);
5537  visual_wheel.cnode->attachObject(ec);
5538  }
5539  catch (...)
5540  {
5541  std::stringstream msg;
5542  msg << "Failed to load mesh '" << wheel_mesh_name.str() << "'";
5543  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_ERROR, msg.str());
5544  }
5545 }

5547 unsigned int RigSpawner::AddWheelBeam(
5548  node_t *node_1,
5549  node_t *node_2,
5550  float spring,
5551  float damping,
5552  boost::shared_ptr<RigDef::BeamDefaults> beam_defaults,
5553  float max_contraction, /* Default: -1.f */
5554  float max_extension, /* Default: -1.f */
5555  int type /* Default: BEAM_INVISIBLE */
5556 )
5557 {
5558  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
5559 
5560  unsigned int index = m_rig->free_beam;
5561  beam_t & beam = AddBeam(*node_1, *node_2, beam_defaults, DEFAULT_DETACHER_GROUP);
5562  beam.type = type;
5563  beam.k = spring;
5564  beam.d = damping;
5565  beam.diameter = DEFAULT_BEAM_DIAMETER;
5566  if (max_contraction > 0.f)
5567  {
5568  beam.shortbound = max_contraction;
5569  beam.longbound = max_extension;
5570  beam.bounded = SHOCK1;
5571  }
5572  CalculateBeamLength(beam);
5573 
5574  if (type != BEAM_VIRTUAL)
5575  {
5576  /* Create visuals, but don't attach to scene-graph (compatibility with show-skeleton function) */
5577  CreateBeamVisuals(beam, index, beam_defaults, false);
5578  }
5579 
5580  return index;
5581 }

5643 void RigSpawner::ProcessWheel2(RigDef::Wheel2 & def)

5664 
5665 void RigSpawner::ProcessSlopeBrake(RigDef::SlopeBrake & def)
5666 {
5667  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
5668 
5669  // #1: regulating_force
5670  float force = def.regulating_force;
5671  if (force < 0.f || force > 20.f)
5672  {
5673  std::stringstream msg;
5674  msg << "Clamping 'regulating_force' value '" << force << "' to allowed range <0 - 20>";
5675  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_INFO, msg.str());
5676  force = (force < 0.f) ? 0.f : 20.f;
5677  }
5678  m_rig->slopeBrakeFactor = force;
5679 
5680  // #2: attach_angle
5681  float attach_angle = def.attach_angle;
5682  if (attach_angle < 1.f || attach_angle > 45.f)
5683  {
5684  std::stringstream msg;
5685  msg << "Clamping 'attach_angle' value '" << force << "' to allowed range <1 - 45>";
5686  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_INFO, msg.str());
5687  attach_angle = (attach_angle < 1.f) ? 1.f : 45.f;
5688  }
5689  m_rig->slopeBrakeAttAngle = attach_angle;
5690 
5691  // #3: release_angle
5692  float release_angle = def.release_angle;
5693  if (release_angle < 1.f || release_angle > 45.f)
5694  {
5695  std::stringstream msg;
5696  msg << "Clamping 'release_angle' value '" << force << "' to allowed range <1 - 45>";
5697  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_INFO, msg.str());
5698  release_angle = (release_angle < 1.f) ? 1.f : 45.f;
5699  }
5700  m_rig->slopeBrakeRelAngle = release_angle + attach_angle;
5701 
5702  // Flag
5703  m_rig->slopeBrake = true;
5704 };
5705 
5706 void RigSpawner::ProcessTractionControl(RigDef::TractionControl & def)
5707 {
5708  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
5709 
5710  /* #1: regulating_force */
5711  float force = def.regulation_force;
5712  if (force < 0.f || force > 20.f)
5713  {
5714  std::stringstream msg;
5715  msg << "Clamping 'regulating_force' value '" << force << "' to allowed range <0 - 20>";
5716  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_INFO, msg.str());
5717  force = (force < 0.f) ? 0.f : 20.f;
5718  }
5719  m_rig->tc_ratio = force;
5720 
5721  /* #2: wheelslip */
5722  m_rig->tc_wheelslip = (def.wheel_slip < 0.f) ? 0.f : def.wheel_slip;
5723 
5724  /* #3: fade_speed */
5725  m_rig->tc_fade = (def.fade_speed < 0.1f) ? 0.1f : def.fade_speed;
5726 
5727  /* #4: pulse/sec */
5728  float pulse = def.pulse_per_sec;
5729  if (pulse <= 1.0f || pulse >= 2000.0f)
5730  {
5731  m_rig->tc_pulse = 1;
5732  }
5733  else
5734  {
5735  m_rig->tc_pulse = static_cast <unsigned int> (2000.f / std::fabs(pulse));
5736  }
5737 
5738  /* #5: mode */
5739  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.mode, RigDef::AntiLockBrakes::MODE_ON))
5740  {
5741  m_rig->tc_mode = 1;
5742  }
5743  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.mode, RigDef::AntiLockBrakes::MODE_OFF))
5744  {
5745  m_rig->tc_mode = 0;
5746  }
5747  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.mode, RigDef::AntiLockBrakes::MODE_NO_TOGGLE))
5748  {
5749  m_rig->tc_notoggle = true;
5750  }
5751  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.mode, RigDef::AntiLockBrakes::MODE_NO_DASHBOARD))
5752  {
5753  m_rig->tc_present = false;
5754  }
5755  else
5756  {
5757  m_rig->tc_present = true;
5758  }
5759 };
5760 
5761 void RigSpawner::ProcessAntiLockBrakes(RigDef::AntiLockBrakes & def)
5762 {
5763  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
5764 
5765  /* #1: regulating_force */
5766  float force = def.regulation_force;
5767  if (force < 0.f || force > 20.f)
5768  {
5769  std::stringstream msg;
5770  msg << "Clamping 'regulating_force' value '" << force << "' to allowed range <0 - 20>";
5771  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_INFO, msg.str());
5772  force = (force < 0.f) ? 0.f : 20.f;
5773  }
5774  m_rig->alb_ratio = force;
5775 
5776  /* #2: min_speed */
5777  /* Wheelspeed adaption: 60 sec * 60 mins / 1000(kilometer) = 3.6 to get meter per sec */
5778  float min_speed = def.min_speed / 3.6f;
5779  m_rig->alb_minspeed = std::max(0.5f, min_speed);
5780 
5781  /* #3: pulse_per_sec */
5782  float pulse = def.pulse_per_sec;
5783  if (pulse <= 1.0f || pulse >= 2000.0f)
5784  {
5785  m_rig->alb_pulse = 1;
5786  }
5787  else
5788  {
5789  m_rig->alb_pulse = static_cast <unsigned int> (2000.f / std::fabs(pulse));
5790  }
5791 
5792  /* #4: mode */
5793  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.mode, RigDef::AntiLockBrakes::MODE_ON))
5794  {
5795  m_rig->alb_mode = 1;
5796  }
5797  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.mode, RigDef::AntiLockBrakes::MODE_OFF))
5798  {
5799  m_rig->alb_mode = 0;
5800  }
5801  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.mode, RigDef::AntiLockBrakes::MODE_NO_TOGGLE))
5802  {
5803  m_rig->alb_notoggle = true;
5804  }
5805  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.mode, RigDef::AntiLockBrakes::MODE_NO_DASHBOARD))
5806  {
5807  m_rig->alb_present = false;
5808  }
5809  else
5810  {
5811  m_rig->alb_present = true;
5812  }
5813 }
5814 
5815 void RigSpawner::ProcessBrakes(RigDef::Brakes & def)
5816 {
5817  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
5818 
5819  m_rig->brakeforce = def.default_braking_force;
5820  if (def._parking_brake_force_set)
5821  {
5822  m_rig->hbrakeforce = def.parking_brake_force;
5823  }
5824  else
5825  {
5826  m_rig->hbrakeforce = 2.f * m_rig->brakeforce;
5827  }

5891 void RigSpawner::ProcessEngine(RigDef::Engine & def)
5892 {
5893  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
5894 
5895  /* Process it */
5896  m_rig->driveable = TRUCK;
5897 
5898  /* Process gear list to BeamEngine-compatible format */
5899  /* TODO: Move this to BeamEngine::BeamEngine() */
5900  std::vector<float> gears_compat;
5901  gears_compat.reserve(2 + def.gear_ratios.size());
5902  gears_compat.push_back(def.reverse_gear_ratio);
5903  gears_compat.push_back(def.neutral_gear_ratio);
5904  std::vector<float>::iterator itor = def.gear_ratios.begin();
5905  for (; itor < def.gear_ratios.end(); itor++)
5906  {
5907  gears_compat.push_back(*itor);
5908  }
5909 
5910  m_rig->engine = new BeamEngine(
5911  def.shift_down_rpm,
5912  def.shift_up_rpm,
5913  def.torque,
5914  gears_compat,
5915  def.global_gear_ratio,
5916  m_rig->trucknum
5917  );
5918 
5919  /* Are there any startup shifter settings? */
5920  Ogre::String gearbox_mode = SSETTING("gearbox_mode", "Automatic shift");
5921  if (gearbox_mode == "Manual shift - Auto clutch")
5922  m_rig->engine->setAutoMode(BeamEngine::SEMIAUTO);
5923  else if (gearbox_mode == "Fully Manual: sequential shift")
5924  m_rig->engine->setAutoMode(BeamEngine::MANUAL);
5925  else if (gearbox_mode == "Fully Manual: stick shift")
5926  m_rig->engine->setAutoMode(BeamEngine::MANUAL_STICK);
5927  else if (gearbox_mode == "Fully Manual: stick shift with ranges")
5928  m_rig->engine->setAutoMode(BeamEngine::MANUAL_RANGES);
5929 };

6027 void RigSpawner::ProcessCamera(RigDef::Camera & def)
6028 {
6029  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
6030 
6031  /* Center node */
6032  if (def.center_node.IsValidAnyState())
6033  {
6034  m_rig->cameranodepos[m_rig->freecamera]
6035  = static_cast<int>(GetNodeIndexOrThrow(def.center_node));
6036  }
6037  else
6038  {
6039  m_rig->cameranodepos[m_rig->freecamera] = -1;
6040  }
6041 
6042  /* Direction node */
6043  if (def.back_node.IsValidAnyState())
6044  {
6045  m_rig->cameranodedir[m_rig->freecamera]
6046  = static_cast<int>(GetNodeIndexOrThrow(def.back_node));
6047  }
6048  else
6049  {
6050  m_rig->cameranodedir[m_rig->freecamera] = -1;
6051  }
6052 
6053  /* Roll node */
6054  if (def.left_node.IsValidAnyState())
6055  {
6056  m_rig->cameranoderoll[m_rig->freecamera]
6057  = static_cast<int>(GetNodeIndexOrThrow(def.left_node));
6058  }
6059  else
6060  {
6061  m_rig->cameranoderoll[m_rig->freecamera] = -1;
6062  }
6063 
6064  /* Advance */
6065  m_rig->freecamera++;
6066 };

6080 void RigSpawner::ProcessBeam(RigDef::Beam & def)
6081 {
6082  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
6083 
6084  // Nodes
6085  node_t* nodes[] = {nullptr, nullptr};
6086  nodes[0] = GetBeamNodePointer(def.nodes[0]);
6087  if (nodes[0] == nullptr)
6088  {
6089  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_WARNING, std::string("Ignoring beam, could not find node: ") + def.nodes[0].ToString());
6090  return;
6091  }
6092  nodes[1] = GetBeamNodePointer(def.nodes[1]);
6093  if (nodes[1] == nullptr)
6094  {
6095  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_WARNING, std::string("Ignoring beam, could not find node: ") + def.nodes[1].ToString());
6096  return;
6097  }
6098 
6099  // Beam
6100  int beam_index = m_rig->free_beam;
6101  beam_t & beam = GetAndInitFreeBeam(*nodes[0], *nodes[1]);
6102  beam.disabled = false;
6103  beam.type = BEAM_NORMAL;
6104  beam.detacher_group = def.detacher_group;
6105  beam.k = def.defaults->GetScaledSpringiness();
6106  beam.d = def.defaults->GetScaledDamping();
6107  beam.diameter = def.defaults->visual_beam_diameter;
6108  beam.minendmass = 1.f; // Orig = hardcoded in add_beam()
6109  beam.bounded = NOSHOCK; // Orig: if (shortbound) ... hardcoded in BTS_BEAMS
6110 
6111  /* Deformation */
6112  SetBeamDeformationThreshold(beam, def.defaults);
6113 
6114  beam.plastic_coef = def.defaults->plastic_deformation_coefficient;
6115  beam.default_plastic_coef = def.defaults->plastic_deformation_coefficient;
6116 
6117  /* Calculate length */
6118  // orig = precompression hardcoded to 1
6119  float beam_length = (beam.p1->RelPosition - beam.p2->RelPosition).length();
6120  beam.L = beam_length;
6121  beam.Lhydro = beam_length;
6122  beam.refL = beam_length;
6123 
6124  /* Strength */
6125  float beam_strength = def.defaults->GetScaledBreakingThreshold();
6126  beam.strength = beam_strength;
6127  beam.iStrength = beam_strength;
6128 
6129  /* Options */
6130  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.options, RigDef::Beam::OPTION_i_INVISIBLE))
6131  {
6132  beam.type = BEAM_INVISIBLE;
6133  }
6134  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.options, RigDef::Beam::OPTION_r_ROPE))
6135  {
6136  beam.bounded = ROPE;
6137  }
6138  if (BITMASK_IS_1(def.options, RigDef::Beam::OPTION_s_SUPPORT))
6139  {
6140  beam.bounded = SUPPORTBEAM;
6141  beam.longbound = def.extension_break_limit;
6142  }
6143 
6144  CreateBeamVisuals(beam, beam_index, def.defaults, BITMASK_IS_0(def.options, RigDef::Beam::OPTION_i_INVISIBLE));
6145 }

6147 void RigSpawner::SetBeamDeformationThreshold(beam_t & beam, boost::shared_ptr<RigDef::BeamDefaults> beam_defaults)
6148 {
6149  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
6150 
6151  /*
6152  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
6153  Old parser logic
6154  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
6155 
6156  VAR default_deform = BEAM_DEFORM (400,000)
6157  VAR default_deform_scale = 1
6158  VAR beam_creak = BEAM_CREAK_DEFAULT (100,000)
6159  VAR enable_advanced_deformation = false
6160 
6161 
6162  add_beam()
6163  IF default_deform < beam_creak
6164  default_deform = beam_creak
6165  END IF
6166 
6167  VAR beam;
6168  beam.default_deform = default_deform * default_deform_scale
6169  END
6170 
6171 
6172  enable_advanced_deformation:
6173  READ enable_advanced_deformation
6174 
6175 
6176  set_beam_defaults:
6177  READ default_deform
6178  VAR default_deform_user_defined
6179  READ default_deform_scale
6180  VAR plastic_coef_user_defined
6181 
6182  IF (!enable_advanced_deformation && default_deform < BEAM_DEFORM)
6183  default_deform = BEAM_DEFORM;
6184  END IF
6185 
6186  IF (plastic_coef_user_defined)
6187  beam_creak = 0
6188  END IF
6189 
6190  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
6191  TruckParser2013
6192  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
6193 
6194  VAR beam_defaults
6195  {
6196  default_deform = BEAM_DEFORM
6197  scale.default_deform = 1
6198  _enable_advanced_deformation = false
6199  _user_defined = false
6200  _default_deform_set = false
6201  _plastic_coef_user_defined = false
6202  }
6203 
6204 
6205  set_beam_defaults:
6206  READ beam_defaults
6207 
6208 
6209  add_beam:
6210 
6211  // Init
6212 
6213  VAR default_deform = BEAM_DEFORM;
6214  VAR beam_creak = BEAM_CREAK_DEFAULT;
6215 
6216  // Old 'set_beam_defaults'
6217 
6218  IF (beam_defaults._is_user_defined)
6219 
6220  default_deform = beam_defaults.default_deform
6221  IF (!beam_defaults._enable_advanced_deformation && default_deform < BEAM_DEFORM)
6222  default_deform = BEAM_DEFORM;
6223  END IF
6224 
6225  IF (beam_defaults._plastic_coef_user_defined && beam_defaults.plastic_coef >= 0)
6226  beam_creak = 0
6227  END IF
6228 
6229  END IF
6230 
6231  // Old 'add_beam'
6232 
6233  IF default_deform < beam_creak
6234  default_deform = beam_creak
6235  END IF
6236 
6237  VAR beam;
6238  beam.default_deform = default_deform * beam_defaults.scale.default_deform
6239 
6240  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
6241  */
6242 
6243  // Old init
6244  float default_deform = BEAM_DEFORM;
6245  float beam_creak = BEAM_CREAK_DEFAULT;
6246 
6247  // Old 'set_beam_defaults'
6248  if (beam_defaults->_is_user_defined)
6249  {
6250  default_deform = beam_defaults->deformation_threshold_constant;
6251  if (!beam_defaults->_enable_advanced_deformation && default_deform < BEAM_DEFORM)
6252  {
6253  default_deform = BEAM_DEFORM;
6254  }
6255 
6256  bool plastic_coef_user_defined = BITMASK_IS_1(beam_defaults->_user_specified_fields, RigDef::BeamDefaults::PARAM_PLASTIC_DEFORM_COEFFICIENT);
6257  if (plastic_coef_user_defined && beam_defaults->plastic_deformation_coefficient >= 0.f)
6258  {
6259  beam_creak = 0.f;
6260  }
6261  }
6262 
6263  // Old 'add_beam'
6264  if (default_deform < beam_creak)
6265  {
6266  default_deform = beam_creak;
6267  }
6268 
6269  float deformation_threshold = default_deform * beam_defaults->scale.deformation_threshold_constant;
6270 
6271  beam.default_deform = deformation_threshold;
6272  beam.minmaxposnegstress = deformation_threshold;
6273  beam.maxposstress = deformation_threshold;
6274  beam.maxnegstress = -(deformation_threshold);
6275 }
