6334 void RigSpawner::AddMessage(RigSpawner::Message::Type type, Ogre::String const & text)
6335 {
6336  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
6337 
6338  /* Add message to report */
6339  m_messages.push_back(Message(type, text, m_current_keyword));
6340 
6341  /* Log message immediately (to put other log messages in context) */
6342  std::stringstream report;
6343  report << " == RigSpawner: ";
6344  switch (type)
6345  {
6346  case (RigSpawner::Message::TYPE_INTERNAL_ERROR):
6347  report << "INTERNAL ERROR";
6348  ++m_messages_num_errors;
6349  break;
6350 
6351  case (RigSpawner::Message::TYPE_ERROR):
6352  report << "ERROR";
6353  ++m_messages_num_errors;
6354  break;
6355 
6356  case (RigSpawner::Message::TYPE_WARNING):
6357  report << "WARNING";
6358  ++m_messages_num_warnings;
6359  break;
6360 
6361  default:
6362  report << "INFO";
6363  ++m_messages_num_other;
6364  break;
6365  }
6366  report << " (Keyword " << RigDef::File::KeywordToString(m_current_keyword) << ") " << text;
6367  Ogre::LogManager::getSingleton().logMessage(report.str());
6368 }
6369 
6370 std::pair<unsigned int, bool> RigSpawner::GetNodeIndex(RigDef::Node::Ref const & node_ref, bool quiet /* Default: false */)
6371 {
6372  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
6373 
6374  if (!node_ref.IsValidAnyState())
6375  {
6376  if (! quiet)
6377  {
6378  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_ERROR, std::string("Attempt to resolve invalid node reference: ") + node_ref.ToString());
6379  }
6380  return std::make_pair(0, false);
6381  }
6382  bool is_imported = node_ref.GetImportState_IsValid();
6383  bool is_named = (is_imported ? node_ref.GetImportState_IsResolvedNamed() : node_ref.GetRegularState_IsNamed());
6384  if (is_named)
6385  {
6386  auto result = m_named_nodes.find(node_ref.Str());
6387  if (result != m_named_nodes.end())
6388  {
6389  return std::make_pair(result->second, true);
6390  }
6391  else if (! quiet)
6392  {
6393  std::stringstream msg;
6394  msg << "Failed to resolve node-ref (node not found):" << node_ref.ToString();
6395  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_ERROR, msg.str());
6396  }
6397  return std::make_pair(0, false);
6398  }
6399  else
6400  {
6401  // Imported nodes pass without check
6402  if (!is_imported && (node_ref.Num() >= static_cast<unsigned int>(m_rig->free_node)))
6403  {
6404  if (! quiet)
6405  {
6406  std::stringstream msg;
6407  msg << "Failed to resolve node-ref (node index too big, node count is: "<<m_rig->free_node<<"): " << node_ref.ToString();
6408  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_ERROR, msg.str());
6409  }
6410  return std::make_pair(0, false);
6411  }
6412  return std::make_pair(node_ref.Num(), true);
6413  }
6414 }
6415 
6416 node_t* RigSpawner::GetNodePointer(RigDef::Node::Ref const & node_ref)
6417 {
6418  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
6419 
6420  std::pair<unsigned int, bool> result = GetNodeIndex(node_ref);
6421  if (result.second)
6422  {
6423  return & m_rig->nodes[result.first];
6424  }
6425  else
6426  {
6427  return nullptr;
6428  }
6429 }
6430 
6431 node_t* RigSpawner::GetNodePointerOrThrow(RigDef::Node::Ref const & node_ref)
6432 {
6433  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
6434 
6435  node_t *node = GetNodePointer(node_ref);
6436  if (node == nullptr)
6437  {
6438  std::stringstream msg;
6439  msg << "Required node not found: " << node_ref.ToString();
6440  throw Exception(msg.str());
6441  }
6442  return node;
6443 }
6444 
6445 std::pair<unsigned int, bool> RigSpawner::AddNode(RigDef::Node::Id & id)
6446 {
6447  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
6448 
6449  if (!id.IsValid())
6450  {
6451  std::stringstream msg;
6452  msg << "Attempt to add node with 'INVALID' flag: " << id.ToString() << " (number of nodes at this point: " << m_rig->free_node << ")";
6453  this->AddMessage(Message::TYPE_ERROR, msg.str());
6454  return std::make_pair(0, false);
6455  }
6456  if ((m_rig->free_node + 1) > MAX_NODES)
6457  {
6458  std::stringstream msg;
6459  msg << "Node limit (" << MAX_NODES << ") exceeded with node: " << id.ToString();
6460  this->AddMessage(Message::TYPE_ERROR, msg.str());
6461  return std::make_pair(0, false);
6462  }
6463  if (id.IsTypeNamed())
6464  {
6465  unsigned int new_index = static_cast<unsigned int>(m_rig->free_node);
6466  auto insert_result = m_named_nodes.insert(std::make_pair(id.Str(), new_index));
6467  if (! insert_result.second)
6468  {
6469  std::stringstream msg;
6470  msg << "Ignoring named node! Duplicate name: " << id.Str() << " (number of nodes at this point: " << m_rig->free_node << ")";
6471  this->AddMessage(Message::TYPE_ERROR, msg.str());
6472  return std::make_pair(0, false);
6473  }
6474  m_rig->free_node++;
6475  return std::make_pair(new_index, true);
6476  }
6477  if (id.IsTypeNumbered())
6478  {
6479  if (id.Num() < static_cast<unsigned int>(m_rig->free_node))
6480  {
6481  std::stringstream msg;
6482  msg << "Duplicate node number, previous definition will be overriden! - " << id.ToString() << " (number of nodes at this point: " << m_rig->free_node << ")";
6483  this->AddMessage(Message::TYPE_WARNING, msg.str());
6484  }
6485  unsigned int new_index = static_cast<unsigned int>(m_rig->free_node);
6486  m_rig->free_node++;
6487  return std::make_pair(new_index, true);
6488  }
6489  // Invalid node ID without type flag!
6490  throw Exception("Invalid Node::Id without type flags!");
6491 }
6492 
6493 void RigSpawner::ProcessNode(RigDef::Node & def)
6494 {
6495  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
6496 
6497  std::pair<unsigned int, bool> inserted_node = AddNode(def.id);
6498  if (! inserted_node.second)
6499  {
6500  return;
6501  }
6502 
6503  node_t & node = m_rig->nodes[inserted_node.first];
6504  node.pos = inserted_node.first; /* Node index */
6505  node.id = static_cast<int>(def.id.Num());
6506 
6507  /* Positioning */
6508  Ogre::Vector3 node_position = m_spawn_position + m_spawn_rotation * def.position;
6509  node.AbsPosition = node_position;
6510  node.RelPosition = node_position - m_rig->origin;
6511  node.smoothpos = node_position;
6512  node.iPosition = node_position;
6513  if (node.pos != 0)
6514  {
6515  node.iDistance = (m_rig->nodes[0].AbsPosition - node_position).squaredLength();
6516  }
6517 
6518  node.wetstate = DRY; // orig = hardcoded (init_node)
6519  node.wheelid = -1; // Hardcoded in orig (bts_nodes, call to init_node())
6520  node.friction_coef = def.node_defaults->friction;
6521  node.volume_coef = def.node_defaults->volume;
6522  node.surface_coef = def.node_defaults->surface;
6523  node.collisionBoundingBoxID = -1; // orig = hardcoded (init_node)
6524  node.iIsSkin = true; // orig = hardcoded (bts_nodes)
6525 
6526  /* Mass */
6527  if (def.node_defaults->load_weight >= 0.f) // The >= operator is in orig.
6528  {
6529  // orig = further override of hardcoded default.
6530  node.mass = def.node_defaults->load_weight;
6531  node.masstype = NODE_LOADED;
6532  node.overrideMass = true;
6533  }
6534  else
6535  {
6536  node.mass = 10; // Hardcoded in original (bts_nodes, call to init_node())
6537  node.masstype = NODE_NORMAL; // orig = hardcoded (bts_nodes)
6538  }
6539 
6540  /* Gravity */
6541  float gravity = -9.81f;
6542  if(gEnv->terrainManager)
6543  {
6544  gravity = gEnv->terrainManager->getGravity();
6545  }
6546  node.gravimass = Ogre::Vector3(0, node.mass * gravity, 0);
6547 
6548  /* Lockgroup */
6549  node.lockgroup = (m_file->lockgroup_default_nolock) ? RigDef::Lockgroup::LOCKGROUP_NOLOCK : RigDef::Lockgroup::LOCKGROUP_DEFAULT;
6550 
6551  /* Options */
6552  unsigned int options = def.options | def.node_defaults->options; /* Merge bit flags */
6553  if (BITMASK_IS_1(options, RigDef::Node::OPTION_l_LOAD_WEIGHT))
6554  {
6555  if (def._has_load_weight_override)
6556  {
6557  node.masstype = NODE_LOADED;
6558  node.overrideMass = true;
6559  node.mass = def.load_weight_override;
6560  }
6561  else
6562  {
6563  node.masstype = NODE_LOADED;
6564  m_rig->masscount++;
6565  }
6566  }
6567  if (BITMASK_IS_1(options, RigDef::Node::OPTION_e_TERRAIN_EDIT_POINT))
6568  {
6569  if(! m_rig->networking)
6570  {
6571  m_rig->editorId = node.pos;
6572  }
6573  }
6574  if (BITMASK_IS_1(options, RigDef::Node::OPTION_h_HOOK_POINT))
6575  {
6576  /* Link [current-node] -> [node-0] */
6577  /* If current node is 0, link [node-0] -> [node-1] */
6578  node_t & node_2 = (node.pos == 0) ? GetNode(1) : GetNode(0);
6579  unsigned int beam_index = m_rig->free_beam;
6580 
6581  beam_t & beam = AddBeam(node, node_2, def.beam_defaults, def.detacher_group);
6582  SetBeamStrength(beam, def.beam_defaults->GetScaledBreakingThreshold() * 100.f);
6583  beam.type = BEAM_HYDRO;
6584  beam.d = def.beam_defaults->GetScaledDamping() * 0.1f;
6585  beam.k = def.beam_defaults->GetScaledSpringiness();
6586  beam.bounded = ROPE;
6587  beam.disabled = true;
6588  beam.L = HOOK_RANGE_DEFAULT;
6589  beam.Lhydro = HOOK_RANGE_DEFAULT;
6590  beam.refL = HOOK_RANGE_DEFAULT;
6591  beam.commandRatioShort = HOOK_SPEED_DEFAULT;
6592  beam.commandRatioLong = HOOK_SPEED_DEFAULT;
6593  beam.commandShort = 0.0f;
6594  beam.commandLong = 1.0f;
6595  beam.maxtiestress = HOOK_FORCE_DEFAULT;
6596  beam.diameter = DEFAULT_BEAM_DIAMETER;
6597  SetBeamDeformationThreshold(beam, def.beam_defaults);
6598  CreateBeamVisuals(beam, beam_index, def.beam_defaults, false);
6599 
6600  // Logic cloned from SerializedRig.cpp, section BTS_NODES
6601  hook_t hook;
6602  hook.hookNode = & node;
6603  hook.group = -1;
6604  hook.locked = UNLOCKED;
6605  hook.lockNode = 0;
6606  hook.lockTruck = 0;
6607  hook.lockNodes = true;
6608  hook.lockgroup = -1;
6609  hook.beam = & beam;
6610  hook.maxforce = HOOK_FORCE_DEFAULT;
6611  hook.lockrange = HOOK_RANGE_DEFAULT;
6612  hook.lockspeed = HOOK_SPEED_DEFAULT;
6613  hook.selflock = false;
6614  hook.nodisable = false;
6615  hook.timer = 0.0f;
6616  hook.timer_preset = HOOK_LOCK_TIMER_DEFAULT;
6617  hook.autolock = false;
6618  hook.is_hook_visible = false;
6619  m_rig->hooks.push_back(hook);
6620  }
6621  AdjustNodeBuoyancy(node, def, def.node_defaults);
6622  node.mouseGrabMode = (def.options == 0u) ? 2 : node.mouseGrabMode; // 2 = n = mouse grab enabled
6623  node.mouseGrabMode = BITMASK_IS_1(options, RigDef::Node::OPTION_n_MOUSE_GRAB) ? 2 : node.mouseGrabMode;
6624  node.mouseGrabMode = BITMASK_IS_1(options, RigDef::Node::OPTION_m_NO_MOUSE_GRAB) ? 1 : node.mouseGrabMode;
6625  node.contactless = BITMASK_IS_1(options, RigDef::Node::OPTION_c_NO_GROUND_CONTACT) ? 1 : 0;
6626  node.disable_particles = BITMASK_IS_1(options, RigDef::Node::OPTION_p_NO_PARTICLES);
6627  node.disable_sparks = BITMASK_IS_1(options, RigDef::Node::OPTION_f_NO_SPARKS);
6628 
6629  m_rig->smokeRef = BITMASK_IS_1(options, RigDef::Node::OPTION_y_EXHAUST_DIRECTION) ? node.pos : 0;
6630  m_rig->smokeId = BITMASK_IS_1(options, RigDef::Node::OPTION_x_EXHAUST_POINT) ? node.pos : 0;
6631 
6632 #ifdef DEBUG_TRUCKPARSER2013
6633  // DEBUG
6634  std::stringstream msg;
6635  msg<<"DBG ProcessNode() pos="<<node.pos<<", id="<<node.id << ", X=" << node.AbsPosition.x << ", Y=" << node.AbsPosition.y << ", Z=" << node.AbsPosition.z;
6636  LOG(msg.str());
6637  // END
6638 #endif
6639 }

6641 void RigSpawner::AddExhaust(
6642  unsigned int emitter_node_idx,
6643  unsigned int direction_node_idx,
6644  bool old_format,
6645  Ogre::String *user_material_name
6646  )
6647 {
6648  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
6649 
6650  if (m_rig->disable_smoke)
6651  {
6652  return;
6653  }
6654  exhaust_t exhaust;
6655  exhaust.emitterNode = emitter_node_idx;
6656  exhaust.directionNode = direction_node_idx;
6657  exhaust.isOldFormat = old_format;
6658 
6659  Ogre::String material_name;
6660  if (user_material_name != nullptr)
6661  {
6662  material_name = *user_material_name;
6663  }
6664  else
6665  {
6666  material_name = "tracks/Smoke";
6667  }
6668 
6669  if (m_rig->usedSkin != nullptr && m_rig->usedSkin->hasReplacementForMaterial(material_name))
6670  {
6671  Ogre::String new_material = m_rig->usedSkin->getReplacementForMaterial(material_name);
6672  if (! new_material.empty())
6673  {
6674  material_name = new_material;
6675  }
6676  else
6677  {
6678  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_INTERNAL_ERROR, "AddExhaust(): Material replacer returned empty string.");
6679  }
6680  }
6681 
6682  std::stringstream particle_sys_name;
6683  particle_sys_name << "exhaust-" << m_rig->exhausts.size() << "-" << m_rig->truckname;
6684  exhaust.smoker = gEnv->sceneManager->createParticleSystem(particle_sys_name.str(), material_name);
6685  if (exhaust.smoker == nullptr)
6686  {
6687  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_INTERNAL_ERROR, "Failed to create exhaust");
6688  return;
6689  }
6690  exhaust.smoker->setVisibilityFlags(DEPTHMAP_DISABLED); // Disable particles in depthmap
6691 
6692 
6693  exhaust.smokeNode = m_parent_scene_node->createChildSceneNode();
6694  exhaust.smokeNode->attachObject(exhaust.smoker);
6695  exhaust.smokeNode->setPosition(m_rig->nodes[exhaust.emitterNode].AbsPosition);
6696 
6697  m_rig->nodes[emitter_node_idx].isHot = true;
6698  m_rig->nodes[direction_node_idx].iIsSkin = true;
6699  m_rig->nodes[emitter_node_idx].isHot = true;
6700  m_rig->nodes[direction_node_idx].iIsSkin = true;
6701 
6702  m_rig->exhausts.push_back(exhaust);
6703 }

6705 bool RigSpawner::AddModule(Ogre::String const & module_name)

6708 
6709  std::map< Ogre::String, boost::shared_ptr<RigDef::File::Module> >::iterator result
6710  = m_file->modules.find(module_name);
6711 
6712  if (result != m_file->modules.end())
6713  {
6714  m_selected_modules.push_back(result->second);
6715  LOG(" == RigSpawner: Module added to configuration: " + module_name);

6722 void RigSpawner::ProcessCinecam(RigDef::Cinecam & def)
6723 {
6724  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
6725 
6726  if (! CheckNodeLimit(1) && ! CheckBeamLimit(8))
6727  {
6728  return;
6729  }
6730 
6731  /* Node */
6732  Ogre::Vector3 node_pos = m_spawn_position + m_spawn_rotation * def.position;
6733  node_t & camera_node = GetAndInitFreeNode(node_pos);
6734  camera_node.contactless = 1; // Orig: hardcoded in BTS_CINECAM
6735  camera_node.wheelid = -1;
6736  camera_node.friction_coef = NODE_FRICTION_COEF_DEFAULT; // Node defaults are ignored here.
6737  camera_node.id = -1;
6738  AdjustNodeBuoyancy(camera_node, def.node_defaults);
6739  camera_node.volume_coef = def.node_defaults->volume;
6740  camera_node.surface_coef = def.node_defaults->surface;
6741 
6742  m_rig->cinecameranodepos[m_rig->freecinecamera] = camera_node.pos;
6743  m_rig->freecinecamera++;
6744 
6745  /* Beams */
6746  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < 8; i++)
6747  {
6748  int beam_index = m_rig->free_beam;
6749  beam_t & beam = AddBeam(camera_node, GetNode(def.nodes[i]), def.beam_defaults, DEFAULT_DETACHER_GROUP);
6750  beam.type = BEAM_INVISIBLE;
6751  CalculateBeamLength(beam);
6752  beam.k = def.spring;
6753  beam.d = def.damping;
6754  beam.diameter = DEFAULT_BEAM_DIAMETER;
6755  CreateBeamVisuals(beam, beam_index, def.beam_defaults, false);
6756  }
6757 
6758  /* Cabin light */
6759  if (m_rig->flaresMode >= 2 && m_rig->cablight == nullptr)
6760  {
6761  std::stringstream light_name;
6762  light_name << "cabinlight-" << m_rig->truckname;
6763  m_rig->cablight = gEnv->sceneManager->createLight(light_name.str());
6764  m_rig->cablight->setType(Ogre::Light::LT_POINT);
6765  m_rig->cablight->setDiffuseColour( Ogre::ColourValue(0.4, 0.4, 0.3));
6766  m_rig->cablight->setSpecularColour( Ogre::ColourValue(0.4, 0.4, 0.3));
6767  m_rig->cablight->setAttenuation(20, 1, 0, 0);
6768  m_rig->cablight->setCastShadows(false);
6769  m_rig->cablight->setVisible(true);
6770 
6771  m_rig->cablightNode = gEnv->sceneManager->getRootSceneNode()->createChildSceneNode();
6772  m_rig->cablightNode->attachObject(m_rig->cablight);
6773  m_rig->cablightNode->setVisible(false);
6774  m_rig->deletion_sceneNodes.emplace_back(m_rig->cablightNode);
6775  }
6776 };

6811 void RigSpawner::ProcessGlobals(RigDef::Globals & def)
6812 {
6813  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
6814 
6815  m_rig->truckmass = def.dry_mass;
6816  m_rig->loadmass = def.cargo_mass;
6817 
6818  if (! def.material_name.empty())
6819  {
6820  Ogre::String material_name = def.material_name;
6821 
6822  /* Check for skin */
6823  if (m_rig->usedSkin != nullptr && m_rig->usedSkin->hasReplacementForMaterial(def.material_name))
6824  {
6825  Ogre::String skin_mat_name = m_rig->usedSkin->getReplacementForMaterial(def.material_name);
6826  if (! skin_mat_name.empty())
6827  {
6828  material_name = skin_mat_name;
6829  }
6830  }
6831 
6832  /* Clone the material */
6833  Ogre::MaterialPtr mat = Ogre::MaterialManager::getSingleton().getByName(material_name);
6834  if (mat.isNull())
6835  {
6836  std::stringstream msg;
6837  msg << "Material '" << material_name << "' defined in section 'globals' not found. Trying material 'tracks/transred'";
6838  AddMessage(Message::TYPE_ERROR, msg.str());
6839 
6840  mat = Ogre::MaterialManager::getSingleton().getByName("tracks/transred");
6841  if (mat.isNull())
6842  {
6843  throw Exception("Vehicle material (or a built-in replacement) was not found.");
6844  }
6845  }
6846  std::stringstream mat_clone_name;
6847  mat_clone_name << material_name << "-" << m_rig->truckname;
6848  mat->clone(mat_clone_name.str());
6849  strncpy(m_rig->texname, mat_clone_name.str().c_str(), sizeof(m_rig->texname));
6850  }
6851 }

7202 void RigSpawner::RecalculateBoundingBoxes(rig_t *rig)
7203 {
7204  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
7205 
7206  Ogre::Vector3 node_0_pos = rig->nodes[0].AbsPosition;
7207  rig->boundingBox.setExtents(
7208  node_0_pos.x, node_0_pos.y, node_0_pos.z,
7209  node_0_pos.x, node_0_pos.y, node_0_pos.z
7210  );
7211  rig->collisionBoundingBoxes.clear();
7212 
7213  for (int i=0; i < rig->free_node; i++)
7214  {
7215  node_t & node = rig->nodes[i];
7216  Ogre::Vector3 node_position = node.AbsPosition;
7217  rig->boundingBox.merge(node_position);
7218  if (node.collisionBoundingBoxID >= 0)
7219  {
7220  if ((unsigned int) node.collisionBoundingBoxID >= rig->collisionBoundingBoxes.size())
7221  {
7222  rig->collisionBoundingBoxes.push_back(
7223  Ogre::AxisAlignedBox(
7224  node_position.x, node_position.y, node_position.z,
7225  node_position.x, node_position.y, node_position.z
7226  )
7227  );
7228  }
7229  else
7230  {
7231  rig->collisionBoundingBoxes[node.collisionBoundingBoxID].merge(node_position);
7232  }
7233  }
7234  }
7235 
7236  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < rig->collisionBoundingBoxes.size(); i++)
7237  {
7238  rig->collisionBoundingBoxes[i].setMinimum(rig->collisionBoundingBoxes[i].getMinimum() - Ogre::Vector3(0.05f, 0.05f, 0.05f));
7239  rig->collisionBoundingBoxes[i].setMaximum(rig->collisionBoundingBoxes[i].getMaximum() + Ogre::Vector3(0.05f, 0.05f, 0.05f));
7240  }
7241 
7242  rig->boundingBox.setMinimum(rig->boundingBox.getMinimum() - Ogre::Vector3(0.05f, 0.05f, 0.05f));
7243  rig->boundingBox.setMaximum(rig->boundingBox.getMaximum() + Ogre::Vector3(0.05f, 0.05f, 0.05f));
7244 
7245  rig->predictedBoundingBox = rig->boundingBox;
7246  rig->predictedCollisionBoundingBoxes = rig->collisionBoundingBoxes;
7247 }

7249 
7250 void RigSpawner::SetupDefaultSoundSources(Beam *vehicle)
7251 {
7252  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
7253 
7254  int trucknum = vehicle->trucknum;
7255  int smokeId = vehicle->smokeId;
7256 
7257 #ifdef USE_OPENAL
7258  if (SoundScriptManager::getSingleton().isDisabled())
7259  {
7260  return;
7261  }
7262 
7263  //engine
7264  if (vehicle->engine != nullptr) /* Land vehicle */
7265  {
7266  if (vehicle->engine->type=='t')
7267  {
7268  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_diesel", smokeId);
7269  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_force", smokeId);
7270  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_brakes", 0);
7271  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_parkbrakes", 0);
7272  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_reverse_beep", 0);
7273  }
7274  if (vehicle->engine->type=='c')
7275  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_car", smokeId);
7276  if (vehicle->engine->hasturbo)
7277  {
7278  if (vehicle->engine->turboInertiaFactor >= 3)
7279  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_turbo_big", smokeId);
7280  else if (vehicle->engine->turboInertiaFactor <= 0.5)
7281  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_turbo_small", smokeId);
7282  else
7283  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_turbo_mid", smokeId);
7284 
7285  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_turbo_bov", smokeId);
7286  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_wastegate_flutter", smokeId);
7287  }
7288 
7289  if (vehicle->engine->hasair)
7290  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_air_purge", 0);
7291  //starter
7292  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_starter", 0);
7293  // turn signals
7294  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_turn_signal", 0);
7295  }
7296  if (vehicle->driveable==TRUCK)
7297  {
7298  //horn
7299  if (vehicle->ispolice)
7300  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_police", 0);
7301  else
7302  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_horn", 0);
7303  //shift
7304  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_shift", 0);
7305  }
7306  //pump
7307  if (vehicle->hascommands)
7308  {
7309  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_pump", 0);
7310  }
7311  //antilock brake
7312  if (vehicle->alb_present)
7313  {
7314  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_antilock", 0);
7315  }
7316  //tractioncontrol
7317  if (vehicle->tc_present)
7318  {
7319  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_tractioncontrol", 0);
7320  }
7321  //screetch
7322  if ((vehicle->driveable==TRUCK || vehicle->driveable==AIRPLANE) && vehicle->free_wheel != 0)
7323  {
7324  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_screetch", 0);
7325  }
7326  //break & creak
7327  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_break", 0);
7328  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_creak", 0);
7329  //boat engine
7330  if (vehicle->driveable==BOAT)
7331  {
7332  if (vehicle->totalmass>50000.0)
7333  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_marine_large", smokeId);
7334  else
7335  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_marine_small", smokeId);
7336  //no start/stop engine for boats, so set sound always on!
7337  SoundScriptManager::getSingleton().trigStart(trucknum, SS_TRIG_ENGINE);
7338  SoundScriptManager::getSingleton().modulate(trucknum, SS_MOD_ENGINE, 0.5);
7339  }
7340  //airplane warnings
7341  if (vehicle->driveable==AIRPLANE)
7342  {
7343  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_gpws_10", 0);
7344  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_gpws_20", 0);
7345  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_gpws_30", 0);
7346  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_gpws_40", 0);
7347  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_gpws_50", 0);
7348  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_gpws_100", 0);
7349 
7350  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_gpws_pullup", 0);
7351  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_gpws_minimums", 0);
7352  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_gpws_apdisconnect", 0);
7353  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_aoa_warning", 0);
7354 
7355  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_aivionic_chat01", 0);
7356  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_aivionic_chat02", 0);
7357  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_aivionic_chat03", 0);
7358  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_aivionic_chat04", 0);
7359  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_aivionic_chat05", 0);
7360  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_aivionic_chat06", 0);
7361  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_aivionic_chat07", 0);
7362  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_aivionic_chat08", 0);
7363  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_aivionic_chat09", 0);
7364  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_aivionic_chat10", 0);
7365  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_aivionic_chat11", 0);
7366  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_aivionic_chat12", 0);
7367  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_aivionic_chat13", 0);
7368  }
7369  //airplane engines
7370  for (int i=0; i<vehicle->free_aeroengine && i<8; i++)
7371  {
7372  int turbojet_node = vehicle->aeroengines[i]->getNoderef();
7373  Ogre::String index_str = TOSTRING(i+1);
7374 
7375  if (vehicle->aeroengines[i]->getType()==AeroEngine::AEROENGINE_TYPE_TURBOJET)
7376  {
7377  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_turbojet_start" + index_str, turbojet_node);
7378  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_turbojet_lopower" + index_str, turbojet_node);
7379  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_turbojet_hipower" + index_str, turbojet_node);
7380  if (((Turbojet*)(vehicle->aeroengines[i]))->afterburnable)
7381  {
7382  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_turbojet_afterburner" + index_str, turbojet_node);
7383  }
7384  }
7385  else if (vehicle->aeroengines[i]->getType()==AeroEngine::AEROENGINE_TYPE_TURBOPROP)
7386  {
7387  if (((Turboprop*)vehicle->aeroengines[i])->is_piston)
7388  {
7389  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_pistonprop_start" + index_str, turbojet_node);
7390  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_pistonprop_lopower" + index_str, turbojet_node);
7391  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_pistonprop_hipower" + index_str, turbojet_node);
7392  }
7393  else
7394  {
7395  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_turboprop_start" + index_str, turbojet_node);
7396  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_turboprop_lopower" + index_str, turbojet_node);
7397  AddSoundSourceInstance(vehicle, "tracks/default_turboprop_hipower" + index_str, turbojet_node);
7398  }
7399  }
7400  }
7401 
7402  // linked sounds
7403  for (int i=0; i<vehicle->free_commands; i++)
7404  {
7405  AddSoundSource(vehicle, SoundScriptManager::getSingleton().createInstance(Ogre::String("tracks/linked/default_command/extend"), trucknum, NULL, SL_COMMAND, i), 0);
7406  AddSoundSource(vehicle, SoundScriptManager::getSingleton().createInstance(Ogre::String("tracks/linked/default_command/retract"), trucknum, NULL, SL_COMMAND, -i), 0);
7407  }
7408 
7409 #endif //OPENAL
7410 }

7412 void RigSpawner::UpdateCollcabContacterNodes()
7413 {
7414  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
7415 
7416  for (int i=0; i<m_rig->free_collcab; i++)
7417  {

7421  m_rig->nodes[m_rig->cabs[tmpv+2]].contacter = true;
7422  }
7423 }

7425 std::string RigSpawner::ProcessMessagesToString()
7426 {
7427  SPAWNER_PROFILE_SCOPED();
7428 
7429  std::stringstream report;
7430 
7431  auto itor = m_messages.begin();
7432  auto end = m_messages.end();
7433  for (; itor != end; ++itor)
7434  {
7435  switch (itor->type)
7436  {
7437  case (Message::TYPE_INTERNAL_ERROR):
7438  report << "#FF3300 INTERNAL ERROR #FFFFFF";
7439  break;
7440 
7441  case (Message::TYPE_ERROR):
7442  report << "#FF3300 ERROR #FFFFFF";
7443  break;
7444 
7445  case (Message::TYPE_WARNING):
7446  report << "#FFFF00 WARNING #FFFFFF";
7447  break;
7448 
7449  default:
7450  report << "INFO";
7451  break;
7452  }
7453  report << "(Keyword " << RigDef::File::KeywordToString(itor->keyword) << ")" << std::endl;
7454  report << "\t" << itor->text << std::endl;
7455  }
7456  return report.str();
7457 }
